\id 1SA Pohnpeian Bible
\h 1 SAMUEL
\toc1 1 SAMUEL
\toc2 1 SAMUEL
\toc3 1 Sam.
\mt1 1 SAMUEL
\is1 Oaralap en Pwuhk wet
\ip \bk Keieun Pwuken Samuel \bk* koasoia duwen wiewia kan me pweida nan irair en ahnsou nanpwungen mwehin sounkopwung kan oh mwehin nanmwarki kan nan wehin Israel. Wekidekla wet nan mouren wehin Israel pidada ohl kesempwal silimen: Samuel, iei ih me wia kaimwseklahn sounkopwung lapalap ako; Sohl, ih me tepin nanmwarkien Israel; oh Depit, me eh mwekid kan mwohn eh wiahla nanmwarki kin iang pwarada nan koasoiepen mouren Samuel oh Sohl.
\ip Oaralap kesempwal en pwuhk wet, duwehte oaralap kesempwal en pwuken poadopoad teikan en Kedehde Mering, iei duwen loalopwoatohng Koht eh kin kahrehda pweida mwahu, a sapeik kin kahrehda paisuwed. Met dehdedahr mehlel sang ni mahsen en Kaun-o ong samworo Ilai nan ire laud 2.30 me mahsanih, “I pahn kin kawauwihala irail kan me kin waunekin ie, oh I pahn kin mwamwahliki irail kan me kin mwamwahlikin ie.”
\ip Pwuhk wet kasalehda duwen peikasal en mehn Israel ko ong ni koasoandien mwehin nanmwarki kan. Pwe Kaun-o me kin wia uhdahn nanmwarkien Israel, ahpw e ketin pilohng irail arail nanmwarki pwehki ar pekipeki. Ahpw me keieu kesempwal, duwen nanmwarki oh mehn Israel kan, ar kin mihmi pahn manaman oh kadeikpen Koht (2.7-10). Nin duwen kosonned en Koht pwungen aramas koaros me semwehmwe oh kepwehpwe kan, pahn duweduwehte.
\iot Audepe ni Oaralap
\io1 Duwen Samuel eh wia sounkopwung en Israel 1.1—7.17
\io1 Sohl wiahla nanmwarki 8.1—10.27
\io1 Keieun sounpar akan en mwehin Sohl 11.1—15.35
\io1 Depit oh Samuel 16.1—30.31
\io1 Sipallahn Sohl oh sapwellime pwutak kan 31.1-13
\c 1
\s1 Elkana oh Eh Peneinei nan Sailo
\p 
\v 1 Mie ohl emen me kisehn Epraim me ede Elkana, me kin kousoan nan kahnimw Rama, nan sahpw nahnahn Epraim. Eh pahpa, iei Seroham, oh eh pahpa kahlap iei Elihu, kisehn peneineien Tohu, apali en peneineien Sup.
\v 2 Elkana pwoudiki lih riemen, Ana oh Penina. Penina me neitik seri, a Ana sohte neitik.
\v 3 Nan sounpar koaros Elkana kin kohla Sailo sang nan eh kahnimwo pwe en iang wia eh kaudok oh meirong ong KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap, wasa me Opni oh Pineas, nein Ilai pwutak riemeno, kin wia samworo en KAUN-O ie.
\v 4 Ahnsou koaros me Elkana pahn kin wia eh meirong, e kin kihong pweisen Penina oh pweisen emenemen nah seri ko sang ni meirongo.
\v 5 Eri mehnda ma e poakepoake mehlel Ana, ahpw e kin kihong uwen pwais en emente aramas, pwehki KAUN-O sohte ketin kupwurehiong nah seri.
\v 6 Eri, Penina kin pelian Ana oh kin epwehnki kaloke oh kasarowe, pwehki KAUN-O eh sohte ketikihong nah seri.
\v 7 Eri, met wiewiawiher erein sounpar tohto. Ahnsou koaros me re kin pwarala nan tehnpas en KAUN-O, Penina kin kansensuwedihada Ana, ih me kahrehda Ana kin sengiseng oh sohla kin men mwenge.
\v 8 Eh pwoudo, Elkana, kin idek reh, “Ana, dahme ke sengisengki? Dahme ke sohte tungoalki? Dahme ke mwomwen nsensuwedki ahnsou koaros? Ke sohte itarkin ie sang omw pahn naineki pwutak ehk?”
\s1 Ana oh Ilai
\p 
\v 9-10 Kedekedeo, mwurin ar tungoal nan tehnpas en KAUN-O, nan Sailo, Ana ahpw uhda, e inenen nsensuwed mehlel; ih eri sengiseng oh kapakapohng KAUN-O. Ni ahnsowo Ilai mwomwohd nan dewe limwahn wenihmwo.
\v 11 Ana ahpw inoukihda kehlail nan kapehde, ketihtihki, “Maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalap, komw ketin mahsanih sapwellimomwi lidu menet! Komw ketin mwahngih ei apwal oh ketin kupwurei ie! Komw dehr ketin likidmelieiehla! Ma komw pahn ketin kupwurehiong ie emen pwutaken, I pahn inoukihda met me I pahn kasarawihong komwi erein eh mour unsek, oh e sohte pahn sehkasang pitenmoange.”\f a \fr 1:11 \fk SOHTE PAHN SEHKASANG PITENMOANGE: \ft Kilel en kasarawihong KAUN-O (tehk Nemp 6.5.)\f*\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Nemp 6.5\x*
\p 
\v 12 Ana eri usehlahte wie kapakapohng KAUN-O ahnsou reirei, a Ilai mwomwohd mwasamwasahn kilin ewe.
\v 13 Ana wie kapakap ni ngihl tikitik; kilin ewe mwekimwekid ahpw sohte ngile. Ihme Ilai kihkihong me e sakaula,
\v 14 ahpw ndahng, “Ke dehr nim wain, pwe ke dehr mwomwen sakau!”
\p 
\v 15 A liho sapeng, ketihtihki, “Soh, maing! I sohte sakau! I pil sohte iang nim wain. I mihmi nan apwal laud, oh I wie kapakap pwe I en kasalehiong KAUN-O ei apwal akan.
\v 16 Komw dehr wiahkin ie lih sohte katepe men. I kin wie kapakap nin duwen mwohmw wet pwehki ei direkilahr nsensuwed.”
\p 
\v 17 Ilai eri sapeng, ketihtihki, “Eri, kohkohwei ni popohl, oh Koht en Israel en ketin kapwaiada omw pekipeken.”
\p 
\v 18 Ana eri nda, “Komw ketin kupwure sapwellimomwi lidu menet ahnsou koaros.” E ahpw kohkohla oh nsenamwahulahr, oh kakehr tungoal.
\s1 Ipwidi oh Kasarawihpen Samuel
\p 
\v 19 Eri, manda sang rahno, Elkana oh eh peneinei ahpw pwourda mwadang oh wia ar kaudok ong KAUN-O. Re ahpw pwurala ni imwarailo nan Rama. Elkana ahpw wiahda nsenen pwopwoud ong eh pwoud Ana. KAUN-O eri ketin kapwaiada en Ana eh pekipeko.
\v 20 Ih eri liseianda oh naitikihada kisin pwutak kis, ih eri kihong ede Samuel;\f b \fr 1:20 \fk SAMUEL: \ft Ahd wet ni mahsen en Ipru wehwehki “mwaren Koht,” e pil ekis duwehte mahsen me wehwehki “pekihda.”\f* pwehki duwen eh ketihtihki, “I patohwan pekidahr rehn KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 21 Eri, e pil lelehr ehu ahnsou me Elkana oh eh peneinei pahn pwurala Sailo pwe re en wiahiong KAUN-O ar meirong me re kin wia nan pahr koaros, oh pil meirong tohrohr me e inoukidahr.
\v 22 Ahpw Ana sohte iang kohla; pwe e ndaiong eh pwoudo, “Mwurin kisin seriet eh pahn mweisang dihdi, I pahn walahng nan tehnpas en Koht, wasa e pahn mihmi ie erein eh mour.”
\p 
\v 23 Elkana eri sapeng, “Kowe me ese dahme keieu mwahu. Eri, kapwaiada, oh mihmihte met, serien lao mweisang dihdi. KAUN-O en ketin kupwure pwe omw inou en pweida.” Ana eri mihmihte ni imweo, apwahpwalih nah serio.
\p 
\v 24 Mwurin eh kamweidsang serio dihdi, e ahpw walahng Sailo, iangahki kisin koupwul wol kis me sounpar siluh, oh pil nesen pilawa ehu, oh ehd kilin mahn me diren wain. Mehnda en pwutako eh tikitiko, a e wahla nan tehnpas en KAUN-O nan Sailo.
\v 25 Irail eri kemehla kouo, a serio re walahng rehn Ilai.
\v 26 Ana eri ndahng Ilai, “Maing, komw kupwur mahk. Komw tamataman ie? Pwe iei ngehi liho me komw mahsanih eh kesikesihnen wasaht oh wie kapakapohng KAUN-O.
\v 27 I peki rehn KAUN-O en ketikihong ie seriet. Eri, iet e ketin kapwaiadahr ei pekipeko.
\v 28 Eri, I pahn patohwan kasarawihong KAUN-O seriet. KAUN-O me pahn ketin sapwellimaniki seri menet erein eh mour.”
\p Irail eri wia ar kaudok ong KAUN-O wasao.
\c 2
\q1 
\v 1 “KAUN-O ketin audehkidahr peren nan kapehdiet,
\q2 ia uwen ei perenki me e ketin wiahiong ieht!
\q1 I kin kouruhrki ei imwintihti kan;
\q2 ia uwen ei peren pwehki eh ketin seweseiedahr!\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Luk 1.46-55.\x*
\b
\q1 
\v 2 “Sohte me sarawi duwehte KAUN-O;
\q2 sohte emen me duwehte ih,
\q2 sohte silepe men me duwehte at Koht.
\q1 
\v 3 Kumwail eri tokedihsang amwail aksuwei;
\q2 kumwail dehr doadoahngki lokaia ileile kan.
\q1 Pwe KAUN-O, iei Koht emen me mwahngih mehkoaros,
\q2 oh kin ketin kadeikada wiewia koaros en aramas akan.
\q1 
\v 4 Nein sounpei dengngan kan kesik ketieu kan timpesengehr,
\q2 a me luwet akan uhd kehlaillahr.
\q1 
\v 5 “Aramas akan me kin mwomwohdte mahs oh tungutungoal;
\q2 met re kin pein kadoahkihada ar tungoal kisin mwenge,
\q2 a me semwehmwe kan solahr kin men mwengehda.
\q1 Lih depweno kaipwidi seri isimen,
\q2 a lih me neitik seri tohto, solahr nah seri.
\q1 
\v 6 Pwe KAUN-O, iei ih me kin ketikihong mour oh ketikihsang,
\q2 ih me kin ketin kadaralahng aramas akan nan wasahn me melahr akan,\f c \fr 2:6 \fk WASAHN ME MELAHR AKAN: \ft Ni ahnsowo aramas akan kin kamehlele me wasahn me melahr akan mie pahn sampah.\f*
\q2 oh ih me kin ketin kapwureiraildo.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Kupw 16.13; Dop13.2.\x*
\q1 
\v 7 E kin ketin kakepwehpwehla ekei oh kin ketin kasemwehmwehla ekei;
\q2 ih me ketin kasapwilada ekei oh kin ketin kasapwilidi ekei.
\q1 
\v 8 Ih me kin ketin pwekada me semwehmwe kan sang nan pwelpar,
\q2 oh kin ketin kasapwilada me paisuwed akan sang nan ar apwal.
\q1 E kin ketin koasoanediong irail re en iang mi rehn me lapalap akan,
\q2 oh kin ketin kamwohdangiraildi nan dehu wahu kan.
\q1 KAUN-O me ketin sapwellimaniki poahsoan kan en sampah;\f d \fr 2:8 \fk POAHSOAN KAN EN SAMPAH: \ft Mehn Ipru kan mahsie kin kamehlele me sampah mi pohn poahsoan kei me mi pahn madau.\f*
\q2 oh e ketin wiahda sampah pohn poahsoan pwukat.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 “E kin ketin apwalih mouren sapwellime aramas loalopwoat akan,
\q2 a me suwed akan e kin ketin kasohrehla nan rotorot;
\q2 pwe sohte aramas emen kin pweida sang ni pein eh kehl.
\q1 
\v 10 Sapwellimen KAUN-O imwintihti kan pahn mwomwla;
\q2 e pahn ketin kauweirailla sang nanleng.
\q1 KAUN-O pahn ketin kadeikada sampah pokon;
\q2 e pahn ketikihong sapwellime nanmwarki manaman,
\q2 e pahn kupwurehda pwe sapwellime nanmwarki me e ketin pilada en powehdi.”
\p 
\v 11 Elkana eri pwurala ni imwe nan Rama; a kisin pwutako mihmihte Sailo, oh wie papah KAUN-O pahn epwelipen samworo Ilai.
\s1 Nein Ilai Pwutak ko
\p 
\v 12 Eri, nein Ilai pwutak ko inenen mwersuwed. Ira sohte mwahn kin nsenohki KAUN-O
\v 13 de kosonned kan duwen pwukoahn samworo kan ong aramas akan. Pwe, ni ahnsou me aramas emen kin wiahda eh meirong, en samworo ko ar laduwo kin wa kohdo nah pwohk kasang siluh, oh nindokon uduk en meirongo kin wie kungkuk,
\v 14 laduwo kin doakoahsang uduko nan einpwoato. Eri, uwen me e kin doakoahsang, e kin walahng samworo ko. Ih soangen tiahk wet me ira kin wiahiong mehn Israel koaros me kin kohdo Sailo pwe re en wia ar meirong wasao.
\v 15 Pil ehu, mwohn ar kin isikala wih en mahn ako, ladun samworo ko kin kohdo oh ndahng aramas me wiewia eh meirongo, “Kihdo ekis uduken, saken samworo ko, pwe I en umwunda. Pwe ira sohte men ale uduk pwoail, ahpw me amas.”
\p 
\v 16 Ma aramaso pahn sapeng, nda, “Kitail isikala mahs wihet, a mwuhr komw kak ale dahme komw inengieng,” ladun samworo ko kin nda, “Soh! Kihdo mette! Pwe ma soh, I pahn adihasang uhk.”
\p 
\v 17 Dipen nein Ilai pwutak riemenet me inenen lapalap mwohn silangin KAUN-O, pwehki ara mwamwahlkihla en aramas akan ar meirong ong KAUN-O.
\s1 Samuel nan Sailo
\p 
\v 18 Kisin pwutak Samuel eri usehla eh doadoahk en papah KAUN-O, e kin likilikawih likou sarawi linen.
\v 19 Eri, sounpar koaros eh nohno kin wiahda kisin likou reirei, oh kin wa kolahng reh ni ih oh eh pwoudo ara kin kolahng wie ara meirong.
\v 20 Ilai eri kin kupwuramwahwih Elkana oh eh pwoud, oh kin ketihtihkihong Elkana, “KAUN-O en ketin kupwurehiong komwi ekei serien, me pahn wiliandi memenet me kumwa kasarawihongehr KAUN-O.”
\p Mwuhr, ira ahpw kin pwurala ni imwara.
\p 
\v 21 KAUN-O eri ketin kupwuramwahwih Ana, oh ketikihong pil nah pwutak silimen oh serepein riemen. Samuel eri kekeirda ni eh papah KAUN-O.
\s1 Ilai oh Nah Pwutak ko
\p 
\v 22 A met Ilai inenen likeilapalahr. E ahpw kin rongorong mehkoaros me nah pwutak ko kin wiewiahiong mehn Israel kan, oh pil duwen ara kin wendi rehn lih akan me kin kodohng doadoahk ni wehnimwen Impwal me KAUN-O pahn kin ketiket loale.
\v 23 Ih eri padahkihong ira, “Dahme kumwa wiewiahki soahng suwed pwukat? Aramas koaros kin ndaiong ie duwen suwed me kumwa wiewia kan.
\v 24 Samwa ko, menlau kumwa tokedihsang amwa wiewia suwed pwukat me aramas koaros kin koasokoasoia duwe!
\v 25 Ma aramas emen pahn wiahda sapwung ehu ong emen tohrohr, Koht kak ketin doarehla; ahpw ihs me kak doarehla aramas me kin wiahda sapwung ong Koht?”
\p Ahpw ira sohte mwahn men rong ara pahpao, pwehki KAUN-O eh ketin kupwuredahr me e pahn kemeirahla.
\p 
\v 26 Kisin pwutak Samuel ahpw kekeirda, oh masamasala mwohn silangin KAUN-O oh pil mwohn aramas akan.\x - \xo 2:26 \xt Sir 46.13; Luk 2.52.\x*
\s1 Kokohp en Kalokolok ong Peneineien Ilai
\p 
\v 27 Soukohp emen eri pwarkidohng Ilai mahsen pwoatet sang rehn KAUN-O: “Ni ahnsou me omw pahpa kahlap ako, Aaron, oh eh peneinei, mihmi Isip wiewia lidun Parao, I kasalehda pein ngehi ong ih.
\v 28 Sang nanpwungen kadaudok koaros en Israel I pilada peneinein Aaron pwe en wiahla ei samworo, oh kin papah ei pei sarawi, isihsik warpwohmwahu, oh likilikawih likou ihpod\f e \fr 2:28 \fk IHPOD: \ft Tehk ni kawehwehpen lepin mahsen kan.\f* mwohn silangi. I pil mweidohng pwaisarail en kohieng irail sang nan meirong isihs ko pohn ei pei sarawio.\x - \xo 2:28 \xt Eks. 28.1-4; b Lip 7.35-36.\x*
\v 29 Eri, dahme kumwail noahrokehki ei meirong kan oh ei kisakis kan, me I koasoanehdi. Ilai dahme ke waunekihki noumw pwutak kan sang ngehi, ni omw kin mweidohng ira en mworouroukihla pali mwahu en meirong kan me aramas akan kin meirongkihong ie?
\v 30 Ngehi, KAUN-O, Koht en Israel, I inoukihong omw peneinei mahso, oh pil ong omw peneinei lap, me kumwail pahn kin papah ie wiewia doadoahk en samworo kohkohlahte. Ahpw ahnsou wet, I koasoanedier me met solahr pahn wiawi! Pwe I pahn kin wauneki irail kan me kin waunekin ie, oh I pahn kin mwamwahliki irail kan me kin mwamwahlikin ie.
\v 31 Eri, ke en ese, pwe ahnsou ehu kohkohdo, I pahn kemehla mwahnakapw koaros en omw peneinei oh omw peneinei lap, sohte ohl emen nan omw peneinei me pahn likeilapala.
\v 32 Ke pahn nsensuwedkihla oh peirinkihda kapai kan koaros me I pahn kihong mehn Israel teikan, a sohte emen nan omw peneinei me pahn pwurehng mour werei.
\v 33 Ahpw metehmen me I pahn mweidohng en momour sang nan kadaudokomw kan, pwe en papah ie nin doadoahk en samworo. Ahpw e pahn maskunla oh sohla eh koapworopwor. Kadaudokomw teikan koaros pahn mehkihla mehla suwed.
\p 
\v 34 Oh ni ahnsou me noumw pwutak riemen, Opni oh Pineas, pahn mehla ni rahnteieu, ih met me pahn kasalehiong uhk duwen me I ndawei kat eh pahn pweida.\x - \xo 2:34 \xt 1 Sam. 4.11.\x*
\v 35 A I pahn pilada samworo men me pahn loalopwoatohng ie oh kapwaiada mehkoaros me I kin kupwurki. I pahn kihong kadaudoke kan, pwe re en kin papah ie ahnsou koaros mwohn silangin nanmwarki me I pahn pilada.
\v 36 Eri, kadaudokomw men me pahn mourla pahn pwarala rehn samworo oh peki mwohni oh ar tungoal kisin mwenge, oh peki en mweimweiong en sewese samworo kan, pwe re en kak tungoale mehkot.”
\c 3
\s1 KAUN-O ketin Pwarohng Samuel
\p 
\v 1 Eri, kisin pwutak Samuel ahpw kin wie papah KAUN-O pahn kaweidpen Ilai. Ni ahnsowo mahsen sang rehn KAUN-O me malaulau mehlel, oh pil kaudiahl sang reh sohte kin kalapw wiawi.
\v 2 Eri, Ilai, ni eh kereniongehr maskunla, pwohng ehu, e ahpw memeir nan eh pere;
\v 3 a Samuel wie memeir nan mwoahl sarawio, wasa sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo mihmi ie. Nin sohrahn, nindokon lampo wie ngkingken, \fig |alt="HK-78D Sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo" src="" size="col" ref="1 SAMUEL 3:3"\fig*
\v 4 KAUN-O ahpw malipe Samuel, a Samuel patohwan sapeng, “Iet ngehi, maing!”
\v 5 E ahpw tangala rehn Ilai oh ndaiong, “Komw me eker ieo; eri, iet ngehi, maing.”
\p A Ilai ahpw sapeng, ketihtihki, “I sohte eker uhk, pwurowei meirla.” Samuel eri pwurala meirla.
\p 
\v 6-7 KAUN-O pil ketin pwurehng malipe Samuel; a kisin pwutako sohte ese me iei KAUN-O mwo, pwe KANU-O sohte kin mahseniong mahs. Ihme e pwourdahte tangala rehn Ilai oh ndaiong, “Komw me eker ieo, iet ngehi, maing.”
\p A Ilai ahpw sapeng, “I sohte eker uhk, samwa; pwurowei meirla.”
\p 
\v 8 KAUN-O ahpw pil ketin malipe Samuel kesilipak; a e pwourdahte tenge Ilai, oh ndaiong, “Komw me eker ieo, iet ngehi, maing.”
\p Ilai eri tehkada me KAUN-O me ketin malimalipe kisin pwutako;
\v 9 ih eri ndahng, “Pwurowei meirla; oh ma mehmen pwurehng eker uhk, a ke sapeng, patohwan, ‘Maing KAUN, komw ketin mahsen, pwe sapwellimomwi laduwet patohwan rongorong.’” Samuel eri pwurala meirla.
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O eri ketido oh ket limwah, oh pil pwurehng malipe duwehte mahs, “Samuel! Samuel!”
\p A Samuel sapeng patohwan, “Maing, komw ketin mahsen, pwe sapwellimomwi ladu patohwan rongorong.”
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O eri ketin mahsanihong, “I pahn wiahiong mehn Israel kan mehkot me inenen kamasepwehk; eri, koaros me pahn rong pahn masepwehkada.
\v 12 Ni rahno, I pahn kapwaiada soahng suwed koaruhsie me I kehkehlingkihong en Ilai eh peneinei.
\v 13 I ndaiong me I pahn kaloke eh peneinei kohkohlahte, pwehki nah pwutak ko ara lahlahwe ie. Ilai ese duwen ara wiewia met, ahpw e sohte katokehdi.
\v 14 Eri, I kahukilahr me sohte meirong de kisakis ehu en Ilai oh eh peneinei pahn kak lapwahda dihp lapalap wet.”
\p 
\v 15 Samuel eri mihmihte nan dewe lel nimenseng. Eri, nimensengo e ahpw pwourda oh ritingada wenihmw en tehnpas en KAUN-O. Ahpw e masak kasalehiong Ilai audepen kaudiahlo.
\v 16 Ilai ahpw ekerodo, ketihtihki, “Samuel!”
\p A Samuel ahpw sapeng, “Iet ngehi, maing.”
\p 
\v 17 Ilai ahpw idek reh, “Dahme KAUN-O mahsanihong uhk? Ke dehr ekihsang ie mehkot. Koht uhdahn pahn ketin kalokeiuk ma ke sohte ndaiong ie mehkoaros me e mahsanihong uhk.”
\v 18 Samuel eri padahkihong Ilai mehkoaros, oh sohte ekihsang mehkot. Ilai eri patohwan, “Iei ih me KAUN-O; e pahn ketin wia mehkoaros me mwahu me e ketin kupwurki.”
\p 
\v 19 Samuel eri kekeirda; oh KAUN-O kin ketin ieiang, oh kin ketin kapwaiada mehkoaros me Samuel kin kohpada.
\v 20 Eri, sang ni irepen sahpwo lel ni irepe teio, mehn Israel koaros eselahr me Samuel uhdahn sapwellimen KAUN-O soukohp emen.
\v 21 KAUN-O eri kin ketin pwarohng oh mahseniong Samuel. Eri, ni Samuel eh kin mahsen, mehn Israel koaros kin rong.
\c 4
\s1 Kohpwahn Inowo Lohdi
\p 
\v 1 Eri, ni ahnsowo mehn Pilisdia ahpw pokonpene pwe re en mahweniong mehn Israel kan. Mehn Israel kan kauwada imwarail impwal kan limwahn Epeneser, a mehn Pilisdia kauwada imwarail impwal akan nan Apek.
\v 2 Mehn Pilisdia kan eri tapihada mahweno, oh mwurin mahwen laud ehu re kalowehdi mehn Israel ko oh kemehla mwehin ele sounpei 4,000.
\v 3 Eri, ni me pitla ko ar leledo ni imwarail impwal ko, kaunen mehn Israel ko ahpw ketihtihki, “Dahme KAUN-O ketin mweidkihong mehn Pilisdia kan en kalowehkinkitaildi rahnwet? Nna, kitail wadohng met Kohpwahn Inowo sang Sailo, pwe KAUN-O en ketin ieiang kitail oh ketin kapitkitailsang atail imwintihti kan.”
\v 4 Irail eri kadarala meninkeder kei Sailo pwe re en wahdo Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap. Kohpwao iei kilel en mwoahl sarawien nanleng. Eri, nein Ilai pwutak riemeno, Opni oh Pineas, ira pil iang Kohpwahn Inowo kohdo.\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Eks 25.22.\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ni Kohpwahn Inowo eh leledo, mehn Israel kan ngihl laudida weriwerki ar peren, ngilarailo ahpw karerehda sampah.
\v 6 Eri, ni mehn Pilisdia kan ar rongada weriwer wet, re ahpw nda, “Soangen mwoarong da ieu met, me wiewiawi nan en mehn Israel kan ar impwal akan?” Eri, ni ar diarada me sapwellimen KAUN-O Kohpwahn Inowo me lelehr nan kahnimpwalen mehn Ipru kan,
\v 7 re ahpw masepwehkada oh nda, “Koht emen me ketier rehrail nan ar kahnimpwalo! Kitail uhdahn pahn sapwungalahr! Soahng wet sohte kin wiahwihong kitail mahs.
\v 8 Ihs me kak doarehsang kitail nin limen koht manaman pwukat? Iei koht pwukat me kemehla mehn Isip ko nan sapwtehno!
\v 9 Eri, kumwail mehn Pilisdia kan, kumwail kommwad! Kumwail mahwen duwehte ohl mehlel. Pwe ma soh, kitail pahn wiahla lidun mehn Ipru kan, duwehte ar wialahr atail lidu mahso. Eri, kumwail mahwen, duwehte ohl mehlel!”
\p 
\v 10 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri mahwen kehlailla. Mehn Israel ko eri lohdi oh tangalahng ni imwarail ko. Mwomwlahn mehn Israel ko me inenen laud, pwe sounpeien Israel 30,000 me kamakamala.
\v 11 Eri, Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O pil lohdiong mehn Pilisdia ko, oh nein Ilai pwutak riemeno, Opni oh Pinead ira kamakamala.
\s1 Mehlahn Ilai
\p 
\v 12 Ohl emen sang ni kadaudok en Pensamin ahpw tangasang nan mahweno tangalahng Sailo; ih eri lel wasao rahnohte. Pwe en kasalehda uwen eh nsensuwed, e tehrpeseng eh likou oh kamwerehdiong pwehl pohn moange.
\v 13 Ilai ahpw wie mwomwohd nan dewe limwahnialo, kilikilenglahng nanialo. Pwe e inenen pwunupwunodki iren Kohpwahn Inowo. Ohlo eri pakairkihda nan kahnimwo rohngo, oh aramas koaros ahpw wiahkihteieu werkihda ar masepwehkada.
\v 14 Ni Ilai eh rongada mwoarongo, e ahpw idek, “Ia wehwehn mwoarong wet?” Ohlo ahpw tangala rehn Ilai pwe en padahkihong duwen rohng wet.
\v 15 (Ahnsowo Ilai sounpar 98, oh e maskunlahr douluhl.)
\v 16 Ohlo eri ndahng, “Rahnwet I tangasang nan mahweno oh tangodohng met.”
\p A Ilai ahpw idek reh, “Samwa, dah rohng? Ia iren mehkoaros?”
\p 
\v 17 A meninkedero ahpw sapeng, nda, “Mehn Israel ko tangasang mehn Pilisdia kan; oh kamwomwomwlahn atail karis kan me inenen mwuledek! A noumwi pwutak ko, Opni oh Pineas, ira kamakamalahr; oh sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo pil lohdier.”
\p 
\v 18 Eri, ahnsou me ohlo ndinda Kohpwahn Inowo, Ilai ahpw saukadahla sang nan dewe limwahn wenihmwo. Eri, pwehki eh likeilapalahr oh mworourou, e pwupwudihte tepinwere timpeseng; ih eri mehla. E wia kaunen Israel erein sounpar 40.
\s1 Mehlahn en Pineas eh Pwoudo
\p 
\v 19 Eri, en Pineas eh pwoudo liseian ahnsowo, oh kereniongehr pahn neitik. Ni eh rongada me sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inoun lohdier, oh duwen en eh pwoudo eh pahpa oh pil eh pwoudo ara melahr, medek en neitik ahpw lel, e ahpw neitik.
\v 20 Ni eh kereniong mehla, sounkeneitiko ahpw ndaiong, “Koapworopwor! Pwe ke naitikihadahr noumw pwutak emen.” Ahpw e sohte men tehk de sapeng.
\v 21 E ahpw kihong eden kisin pwutako Ikapod,\f f \fr 4:21 \fk IKAPOD: \ft Ahd wet ni mahsen en Ipru wehwehki “sohte lingan.”\f* oh kawehwehda, ketihtihki, “Lingan en Koht sohrasangehr Israel!” E nda met pwehki Kohpwahn Inowo eh lohdier, oh pwehki en eh pwoudo eh pahpa oh pil eh pwoudo ara melahr.
\v 22 E pil ketihtihki, “Lingan en Koht sohrasangehr Israel, pwehki sapwellimen Koht Kopwahn Inowo eh lohdier.”
\c 5
\s1 Kohpwahn Inowo Rehn mehn Pilisdia ko
\p 
\v 1 Mwurin mehn Pilsdia kan ar kalowehdi sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo, re wahsang Epeneser walahng nan ar kahnimw Asdod,
\v 2 re ahpw wahlong nan tehnpas en ar koht Dakon, oh koasoanediong limwahn sansalo.
\v 3 Nimenseng en mahndahn rahno mehn Asdod ahpw kilangada duwen sansal en ar koht Dakon eh dikoudihsang nan dewe, dikoudiong nan tahto mwohn sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo. Re ahpw ale sansalo oh pwurehng koasoanediong nan dewe.
\v 4 Pil mandahn rahno, nimensehngie, re kilangada duwen sansalo eh pil pwurehng dikoudihsang nan dewe, dikoudiong mwohn sapwellimen Koht Kohpwahn Inowo. Ahpw moangen sansalo oh peh ko koaros me dolahsang paliwereo mihmi pohn ekipir en wenihmwen tehnpaso. A ihte, tuhkehn sansalo me mihmi limwahn Kohpwan Inowo.
\v 5 (Ihme kahrehda, leledohng rahnwet, samworo kan en Dakon, oh irail koaros me kin pwongih Dakon nan Asdod, ni ar kin pedolong nan tehnpaso, re sohte kin sok pohn wasao, ahpw re kin kahkete powe.)
\p 
\v 6 KAUN-O eri ketin kalokehki mehn Asdod kan kalokolok laud ehu oh ketin kasaloweirailda. Pwe e ketin kaloke irail oh tohn sahpw akan me kapilirailpene ni eh ketin mweidohng pwe soumwahu mpwos\f g \fr 5:6 \fk MPWOS: \ft Soumwahu mpwos iangahki tohtohlahn kitik ni ahnsowohte mwein wehwehki me soumwahu lusulus ehu me tepisang rehn kitik (tehk 6.5).\f* en kohda ni kahwarail kan.
\v 7 Eri, ni ar kilangadahr dahme wiewiawio, re ahpw patohwan, “Koht en Israel ketin kalokalokei kitail iangahki atail koht Dakon. Eri, kitail solahr kak mweidohng Kohpwahn Inowo en mihmi rehtail.”
\v 8 Irail eri kadarapeseng ar sounpakair kan oh kapokonepene nanmwarki limmeno koaros en mehn Pilisdia kan oh idek rehrail, patohwan, “Dahme se pahn wiahiong sapwellimen Koht en Israel Kohpwahn Inowo?”
\p Irail eri sapeng, mahsanih, “En wisikwohng Kad.” Irail eri wahla wasao.
\v 9 Ahpw ni eh lel Kad, KAUN-O pil ketin kalokehki kahnimwo soumwahu ehu me kasalowehda towe kan. Pwe Koht ketin kalokehki soumwahu mpwos me kohda rehn tohn kahnimwo koaros, me laud oh tikitik kan.
\v 10 Irail eri kadaralahng kahnimw Ekron Kohpwahn Inowo. Ahpw ni eh lel wasao, tohn kahnimwo koaros wiahkihteieu werkihda, patohwan, “Re wadohngehr wasaht sapwellimen Koht en Israel Kohpwahn Inowo, pwe en kemeikitailla!”
\v 11 Irail eri pwurehng kapokonepene nanmwarkien Pilisdia kan koaros oh patohwanohng irail, “Kumwail kapwurehwei Kohpwahn Inoun Israel nan uhdahn dewe, pwe en dehr kameikitala oh at peneinei kan.” Eri, lammwi ahpw kipehdi wasa koaros nan kahnimpwalo pwehki kalokolok laud me kin lelohng aramas akan sang nin limmen Koht.
\v 12 Pwe pil ong irail kan me sohte kin iang mehla, soumwahu mpwoso kin lel ni kahwarail kan: eri, re ahpw kin weriwer pekipek sawas sang rehn arail koht akan.
\c 6
\s1 Kasapahldohn Kohpwahn Inowo
\p 
\v 1 Eri, mwurin Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O eh mihmihki nan wehin Pilisdia erein sounpwong isuh,
\v 2 aramas akan ahpw ekerpene samworo kan oh sounakamanaman akan oh idek rehrail, “Dahme kitail pahn wiahiong Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O? Ma kitail pahn kapwurehla nan eh wasa, dahme kitail pahn iangahkihla nin duwen kisakis?”
\p 
\v 3 A re sapeng, nda, “Ma kumwail pahn kapwurehla sapwellimen Koht en Israel Kohpwahn Inowo, kumwail uhdahn pahn iangahkihla kisakis ehu pwe en kapwungala dipamwailo. Kohpwahn Inowo sohte pahn kapwurupwurala ni kisakis ehu eh sohte pahn iang. Pwe iei duwen met amwail pahn mwahula sang amwail soumwahu, oh amwail pahn esehla kahrepen Koht eh ketin kalokalokei kumwail.”
\p 
\v 4 Aramas ako ahpw idek, “A kisakis dah me se pahn iangahkihla?”
\p Re ahpw sapeng, nda, “Mwomwen kitik kohl limau oh mwomwen mpwos kohl limau, ehuehu ong emen nanmwarkien Pilisdia. Pwe soangen soumwahwohte lelohng kumwail oh pil lelohng nanmwarkien Pilisdia ko.
\v 5 Kumwail pahn wiahda mwohmw pwukat en mpwos oh kitik me kaukauwe sapwamwailet, oh sakarkihda dipamwail ong Koht en Israel. Mweinele e pahn ketin katokihedi sapwellime kalokolok ong kumwail, ong amwail koht akan, oh ong sapwamwailet.
\v 6 Kumwail pahn keptakai, duwehte Parao oh mehn Isip ko? Kumwail dehr manokehla duwen Koht eh ketin kaloke irail, re lao mweidala mehn Israel ko en mweselda sang nan Isip.
\v 7 Kumwail eri kaunopada ehu kuruma kapwen, oh kou riemen me saikinte doadoahngki wisik; kumwail eri salihiradiong ni kurumahn, kumwail ahpw kapwurelahng wahra kan nan imwen nahk.
\v 8 Kumwail eri ale Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O oh koasoanediong pohn kurumahn, oh kihdiong mpe ekis kisin kopwahn me audaudkidahr mwohmw kohl ako me kumwail pahn kadaralahng KAUN-O ni mwomwen kisakis mehn kapwungala dipamwail kan. Kumwail ahpw kadar kurumao oh mweidala pwe en pein dahr kohkohwei.
\v 9 Kumwail eri mwasahn; ma e pahn dahr kohwei inenwohngete kahnimw Ped Semes, met pahn wehwehki me Koht en mehn Israel kan me kadaridiong pohtail lapalahn soumwahu suwed wet. A ma soh, eri kitail pahn ese me kaidehkin ih me kadaridi soumwahu wet; ihte soumwahu ehu me lellohng kitail.”
\p 
\v 10 Irail eri kapwaiada dahme koasoandiong irail; re ale kou riemen oh pirehiong ni kuruma ieu, re ahpw salihediong wahra ko nan imwen nahko.
\v 11 Irail eri koasoanediong pohn kurumao Kohpwahn Inowo, iangahki kisin kohpwa me mwohmw kohl en kitik oh mpwos ko mihmi loale.
\v 12 Kou ko eri tapihada mwekid pohn ahl me kolahng Ped Semes, re ahpw tang inentehpwoat, sohte wetsang nanialo. Nanmwarki limmen en mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw idihdawehn kohla lel ni irepen Ped Semes.
\p 
\v 13 Mehn Ped Semes ko wie dondolung wihd ahnsowo nan wahu ehu. Re mwadangete kilangada Kohpwahn Inowo, re ahpw perenkihda kowahlap.
\v 14 Kurumao eri lel nan sapwen Sosua mehn Ped Semes men, oh uhdi wasao limwahn lapalahn takai ehu. Aramas ako eri pelepene tuhkehn kurumao, kemehla kou ko, oh isikala meirongkihong KAUN-O.
\v 15 A mehn Lipai ko ahpw ale Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O oh kisin kohpwa me mwomwen kohl ko mihmi loale, re ahpw koasoanediong pohn takaio. Mehn Ped Semes eri meirongkihong KAUN-O meirong isihs kei oh pil ekei soangen meirong.
\v 16 Nanmwarkien Pilisdia limmeno ahpw mwasamwasahn irail ar wiewia met, re ahpw pwurala Ekron rahnohte.
\p 
\v 17 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri kadaralahng KAUN-O mwomwen mpwos kohl limau nin duwen ar kisakis mehn kapwungala diparail kan; eri, ehuehu sang Asdod, Kasa, Askelon, Kad, oh Ekron.
\v 18 Re pil kadarala mwomwen kitik kohl ko, ehuehu ong kahnimw ko me nanmwarkien Pilisdia limmeno kin kakaun; ong kahnimw koaros me kelpene oh kisin kahnimw kan me sohte kele. Eri, takaio me mi nan sapwen Sosua mehn Ped Semeso, wasa me re koasoanehdi powe Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O, mihmihte wasao lel rahnwet, mehn kadehdehpen dahme pweidahro.
\p 
\v 19 KAUN-O eri ketin kemehla ohlen Ped Semes isiakan, pwehki ar kilenglong nan Kohpwahn Inowo. Aramas ako eri mwahieikin irail, pwehki KAUN-O eh ketin kalokehkin irail soangen kalokolok laud wet.
\s1 Kohpwahn Inowo nan Kahnimw Kiriad Searim
\p 
\v 20 Ohlen Ped Semes ko eri nda, “Ihs me kak uh mwohn silangin KAUN-O, Koht sarawi menet? Ia wasa kitail kak kadaralahng ie pwe kitail en pitsang?”
\v 21 Irail eri kadaralahng sounkair kei rehn tohn kahnimw Kiriad Searim, me ketihtihki, “Mehn Pilisdia kan kapwuredohr Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O. Kumwail kohdihdo ale.”
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Tohn kahnimw Kiriad Searim eri ale Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O oh wahla ni imwen Apinadap, me mi pohn dohl ehu. Irail ahpw kasarawihala nah pwutak Eleasar pwe en kin apwahpwalih Kohpwahn Inowo.\x - \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Sam 6.2-4; 1 Kron 13.5-7.\x*
\s1 Samuel Kaunda Israel
\p 
\v 2 Kohpwahn Inoun KAUN-O eri mihmi nan kahnimw Kiriad Searim ahnsou reirei, kereniong sounpar 20. Erein ahnsowo mehn Israel koaros ahpw kin likweriong KAUN-O pekipeki sapwellime sawas.
\p 
\v 3 Samuel eri padahkihong mehn Israel ko, “Ma kumwail pahn sohpeiong KAUN-O ni mohngiongimwail unsek, eri, kumwail uhdahn pahn kesehla koht koaros en mehn liki kan oh sansal akan en koht lih Asdarde. Kumwail kasarawihong pein kumwail unsek KAUN-O, oh pwongih ihete. Eri, e ahpw pahn kapitkumwailsang pahn manaman en mehn Pilisdia kan.”
\v 4 Mehn Israel ko eri kesehla dikedik kan en ar koht Paal oh Asdarde; re ahpw kin pwongih KAUN-O kelehpw.
\p 
\v 5 Samuel eri ekerpene mehn Israel koaros pwe re en pokonpene Mispa. E ahpw padahkihong irail, “I pahn kapakapkin kumwail rehn KAUN-O wasao.”
\v 6 Irail eri pokonpene Mispa. Re ahpw kihpene pihl oh wudekihdiong nan pwehl wiahki ar mehn meirong ong KAUN-O, re kaisihsol rahno pwon. Re ahpw nda, “Se dipadahr mwohn KAUN-O.” Samuel eri koukousoan Mispa oh kakaun mehn Israel ko.
\p 
\v 7 Ni mehn Pilisdia ko ar rongada me mehn Israel ko pokonpenehr Mispa, nanmwarkien Pilisdia limmeno, iangahki sapwellimarail sounpei ko, mwesella pwe re en mahweniong irail. Ni Mehn Israel ko ar rongada met re masepwehkada;
\v 8 re ahpw ndaiong Samuel, ketihtihki, “Komw dehr tokedihsang omw kasakaskin kiht rehn KAUN-O pwe en ketin doareikitasang mehn Pilisdia kan.”
\v 9 Samuel eri kemehla sihmpwul men oh pwonte isikala pwe en meirongkihong KAUN-O. E ahpw peki rehn KAUN-O en ketin sewese Israel. KAUN-O eri ketin karonge eh pekipek.\x - \xo 7:9 \xt Sir 46.16-18.\x*
\v 10 Pwe nindokon Samuel eh wiewia eh meirongo, mehn Pilisdia ko tapihada mwekid en mahweno. Ahpw ni ahnsowohte, kapitien KAUN-O ahpw ngiriseksang nanleng ong pohn mehn Pilisdia ko. Re ahpw pingida oh tangdoaui.
\v 11 Mehn Israel ko pwakihirailla sang Mispa, re lao lel Pedkar, kemekemeirailla kohla nanialo.
\p 
\v 12 Samuel eri ale takai ehu oh kauwada nanpwungen Mispa oh Sen, e ahpw ketihtihki, “KAUN-O ketin sewesei kitail lao lel wasaht.” Eri, e ahpw kihong eden takaio “Takaien Sawas.”
\v 13 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri lohdi, oh KAUN-O sohla ketin mweidohng irail en pedolong nan sapwen mehn Israel ko nindokon Samuel eh momour.
\v 14 Kahnimw koaros, sang Ekron lel Kad, me mehn Pilisdia ko kalowehdi, ahpw pwurehng mehn Israel. Mehn Israel eri pwurehng ale sahpw koaros me uhdahn sapwarail. Eri, mweimwahu pil miehla nanpwungen mehn Israel oh mehn Kenan.
\p 
\v 15 Samuel eri kakaun mehn Israel erein eh momour.
\v 16 Nan sounpar koaros e kin ketseli oh ketila Pedel, Kilkal, oh Mispa, oh wasa pwukat koaros e kin kapwungala repenpwung kan en mehn Israel.
\v 17 E ahpw kin pwurala ni imwe nan Rama, wasa e pil kin wia ie sounkopwung. E kauwadahng KAUN-O pei sarawi ehu nan Rama.
\c 8
\s1 Mehn Israel Peki emen ar Nanmwarki
\p 
\v 1 Eri, ni Samuel eh likeilapalahr, e ahpw kasapwilada nah pwutak ko pwe ira en wiahla sounkopwung en Israel.
\v 2 Me laudo adaneki Soel, a me tikitiko Apaisa; eri, ira wia sounkopwung nan kahnimw Peersepa.
\v 3 Ahpw ira sohte kin kahlemangih ara pahpao; pwe ira nsenohkihte en kalaudehla neira mwohni. Iei me ira kin ale kisakis laud, oh sohte kin koasoanehdi kopwung kan duwen me konehng.
\p 
\v 4 Sounkaweid koaros en Israel eri pokonpene oh pwarala rehn Samuel nan Rama.
\v 5 Re ahpw patohwanohng, “Komw mahsanih, ahnsou wet komw ketin likeilapalahr, a noumwi pwutak ko sohte kin idawehn omwi kaweid kan. Eri, komw ketin pilada emen nanmwarki me pahn kakaun kiht duwehte sahpw teikan.”
\v 6 Samuel ahpw nsensuwedkihla ar pekipeki nanmwarki men. Ih eri sohpeiong KAUN-O, oh kapakapohng.\x - \xo 8:6 \xt 17.14.\x*
\v 7 KAUN-O eri ketin mahsanihong, “Rong mehkoaros me aramas akan pahn ndaiong uhk. Pwe kaidehk kowe me re soikalahr, pwe ngehi me re soikalahr I en dehr wia ar nanmwarki.
\v 8 Sang ni ahnsou me I kahluwairailsang Isip lel met, re kin sohpeisang ie oh kin kaudokiong koht teikan. Eri, met re pil wiahiong uhk soahngohte me re wiahiong ie.
\v 9 Eri, ke pahn rong irail, ke ahpw pahn kehkehlingkihong irail oh kawehwehiong irail duwen ar nanmwarki kan ar pahn kaunirailda.”
\p 
\v 10 Samuel eri padahkihong mehn Israel ko me pekipeki emen nanmwarki mehkoaros me KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong.
\v 11 E ahpw ketihtihki, “Iet duwen mwomwen amwail nanmwarki me pahn kaunkumwailda. E pahn wiahkihla sounpei noumwail pwutak kan; ekei irail pahn papah nan sapwellime werennanspw akan, a ekei pahn wia sapwellime karis en sounpeien dak oahs, oh ekei pahn wia karis en sounpeien kahmwowe mahwen.
\v 12 E pahn wiahkihla ekei noumwail pwutak kan kaunen sounpei kid, a ekei silepen sounpei limehk. Noumwail pwutak kan pahn kin deipwelih nin lime sahpw akan, kihpene wahnsahpw, oh wiahda tehtehn mahwen oh dipwisoun werennansapw akan.
\v 13 Noumwail serepein kan pahn kin wiahda lehn wai, kukihada kisin mwenge oh umwunda pilawa.
\v 14 E pahn ketikihsang sapwamwail me keieu mwahu kan, amwail mwetin wain kan, oh pil mwetin olip kan; e ahpw pahn ketikihong sapwellime lapalap akan.
\v 15 E pahn ketikihsang eisek kis ehun wahn amwail wahntuhke kan oh wahn amwail mwetin wain kan pwe en ketikihong me lapalap akan en tehnpeseo, oh pil ong sapwellime lapalap teikan.
\v 16 E pahn ketikihsang amwail ladu kan, noumwail kou keieu mwahu kan oh noumwail ahs akan, pwe en kin doadoahngkihong pein ih.
\v 17 E pahn ketikihsang eisek kis ehun noumwail mahn akan. Kumwail pahn wiahla sapwellime lidu.
\v 18 Ni ahnsowo kumwail pahn kaulimala kowahlap pwehki amwail nanmwarkio me kumwail pein pilada; ahpw KAUN-O sohte pahn ketin karongei kumwail.”
\p 
\v 19 Aramas ako ahpw sohte men rong Samuel. Re ahpw ketihtihki, “Soh! Se uhdahn anahne emen nanmwarkien,
\v 20 pwe se en duwehla wehi teikan, en mie at nanmwarki men me pahn kin kakaun kiht oh kin kahluwaikitohng nan mahwen oh kin pepeikin kiht.”
\v 21 Samuel eri rong mehkoaros me re ndaiong, e ahpw patohla oh sakarkidahng KAUN-O.
\v 22 KAUN-O eri ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “Kapwaiada dahme re anahne, oh kihong irail emen nanmwarkien.” Samuel eri padahkihong mehn Israel koaros re en pwuralahng ni imwarail kan.
\c 9
\s1 Sohl Tuhwong Samuel
\p 
\v 1 Mie ohl emen me kisehn kadaudok en Pensamin, ede Kis, nein Apiel, nein Seror, peneineien Pekorad, apali en peneineien Apaia. Eri, Kis ohl kepwehpwe oh ndand emen.
\v 2 Mie nah pwutak emen ede Sohl, mwahnakapw masamwahu men oh kehlail, piht ehu e reireikihsang mwahnakapw teikan en Israel, oh paliwere mwahusang paliwararail koaros.
\p 
\v 3 Eri, ahs ekei, nein Kis, salongala. Ihme Kis ndakihong Sohl, “Ale emen ladu ko, ke ahpw kohwei rapakihdo neita ahs ako.”
\v 4 Sohl oh laduwo eri mwesel kotehla sahpw nahnahn Epraim oh Salisa, ahpw ira sohte diar ahs ako; ira pil douluhllahng nan Saalim, ira pil sohte diar. Ira pil douluhlla nan sapwen Pensamin, ira pil sohte diar.
\v 5 Ni ara lel nan Sup, Sohl ahpw ndaiong laduwo, “Kita pwuralahng ni imwatailo, pwe pahpa pahn sohla pwunodki ahs ako, a e pahn uhd pwunodkinkitahda.”
\p 
\v 6 Laduwo ahpw sapeng, nda, “Komw sepit mahs! Pwe ohl sarawi men mie nan kahnimwet, me inenen wahun rehn aramas koaros, pwehki mehkoaros me e kin kohpada kin pweida. Kita kohla mahs reh, ele e kak ndaiong kita wasa kita kak diar ie ahs ako.”
\p 
\v 7 Sohl eri idek reh, “Ma kita kohla reh, dahme kita kak kisekisehki? Pwehki eh sohte luhwen kanata kisin mwenge kan nan ata ehd en, eri, dahme kita kak kihong?”
\p 
\v 8 Laduwo eri sapeng, nda “Mie rehi sens silper ehu me I kak kihong, e ahpw pahn kak ndaiong kita wasa kita kak diar ie ahs ako.”
\p 
\v 9-11 Eri, Sohl ahpw sapeng, nda, “Me mwahu! Nna, kita!” Ira eri kohla nan kahnimw me ohl sarawio kin kousoan ie. Ni ara kohkohdalahng kahnimwo, ira ahpw tuhwong serepein kei me kohkohdohn idipil. Ira eri idek rehn serepein ko, “Ohl sarawio ketiket nan kahnimwet?”
\p (Mahsie, ahnsou me emen kin men peki rehn Koht mehkot, e kin nda, “Kitail kohla rehn ohl sarawio,” pwehki ni ahnsowo soukohp koaros kin adaneki ohl sarawi.)
\p 
\v 12-13 Serepein ko eri sapeng, nda, “Ei, e ahpwtehn ketiket kohwei. Ma kumwa seimek, kumwa pahn koanoahdi. Kumwa pahn diar ni amwa pahn lelewei nan kahnimwo. E ahpwtehn leledo nan kahnimwet, pwe aramas akan pahn wia ar meirong rahnwet pohn pei sarawio pohn dohlen. Aramas ako me iang lukodohng meirong wet sohte pahn tungoal lao ohlo lel mwo, pwehki e pahn kin ketin kasarawihala mahs meirongo. Ma kumwa kohdahwei ahnsou wet, kumwa pahn diar mwohn eh pahn ketidalahng sak pohn dohlo.”
\v 14 Ira eri kohla nan kahnimwo, oh ni ara pedolong, ira ahpw kilangada Samuel eh ketiket kohieilahng wasahn kaudoko.
\p 
\v 15 Eri, mwohn rahn me Sohl leledohng nan kahnimwo, KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong Samuel,
\v 16 “Lakapw, soangen ahnsou wet, I pahn kadarowohng uhk ohl emen me kisehn kadaudok en Pensamin; keiehdi pwe en wiahla kaunen nei aramas akan en Israel, pwe iei ih me pahn kapitasang irail rehn mehn Pilisdia kan. I kilangehr lokolok en nei aramas akan, oh I rongehr ngilen ar pekipeki sawas.”
\p 
\v 17 Ni Samuel eh kilangada Sohl, KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong, “Ien ohl me I ndaiong uhk duwe. Iei ih me pahn kaunda nei aramas akan.”
\v 18 Sohl eri patohla rehn Samuel limwahn ewen kehlo oh kalelapak reh, “Komw kupwurmahk, oh mahsanihong ie mahs, wasa me ohl sarawio kin kousoan ie.”
\p 
\v 19 Samuel ahpw sapeng, ketihtihki, “Iei ngehi me ohl sarawio. Eri, tiengwei ni wasahn kaudoko. Pwe kumwa riemen pahn iang ie sak rahnwet. Nimenseng en lakapw I ahpw pahn sapeng omw peidek kan koaros oh kadaruhkala.
\v 20 A duwen ahs ako me salongalahr erein rahn siluhwo, ke dehr pwunodki, pwe re dierekier. Ahpw ihs ih me aramas en Israel kan kin kasikasik kowahlap? Iei kowe, oh pil peneineien omw pahpa.”
\p 
\v 21 Sohl eri sapeng, nda, “Ngehi kisehn kadaudok en Pensamin, kadaudok en Israel me keieu tikitik; oh ei peneinei, ih me keieu sohte wede nan kadaudok wet. Eri, dahme komw wiahkihong ie mahsen wet?”
\p 
\v 22 Samuel eri kahrelahng Sohl oh eh laduwo nan pere laud ehu oh kamwohdangirahdiong ni moangen tehpelo, wasa me kerenieng tohnkapar 30 wie mwomwohd ie.
\v 23 Samuel eri padahkihong sounkuko, “Wahdo kisin uduk me I ndaiong uhk ke en katohrehsango.”
\v 24 Sounkuko eri wahdo dengen mahno, oh pwilikihdi mwohn Sohl. Samuel ahpw ketihtihki, “Kilang, iet kisin uduk me wie nekinekiong uhk. Tungoale, pwe I wie nekinekidohng uhk pwe ke en tungoale ahnsou wet, oh iang aramas akan me I lukehdo.”
\p Sohl eri iang Samuel tungoal rahno.
\v 25 Ni ara ketidihsang wasahn kaudoko oh ketlahng nan kahnimwo, re ahpw kaunopadahng Sohl dewe pohn pwelengen ihmwo,\f g \fr 9:25 \fk POHN PWELENGEN IHMW: \ft Ni ahnsowo pohn pwelengen ihmw kan kin patapat, oh aramas akan kin kalap wiahki wasahn arail meir.\f*
\v 26 ih eri meir wasao.
\s1 Samuel Keiehdi Sohl en Wiahla Kaun
\p Nin sohrahn Samuel ahpw eker Sohl ni eh mihmi powe, oh ketihtihki, “Pwourda, pwe I pahn kadaruhkalahr.” Sohl eri pwourda, ih oh Samuel eri wiahkihteieu kohkohla pohn ahlo.
\v 27 Eri, ni ara lel ni irepen kahnimwo, Samuel ahpw ndahng Sohl, “Ndaiong laduwen en tiengwei.” Laduwo eri kohkohla, a Samuel ahpw pil nda, “Awih mahs, pwe I pahn ndaiong uhk dahme Koht ketin mahsanih.”
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Samuel eri ale lehn olip oh kielediong pohn moangen Sohl. E ahpw metik, oh ketihtihki, “KAUN-O ketin keieikomwihdi pwe en wiahla 2kaunen mehn Israel kan. Komw pahn kaunda sapwellime aramas akan oh doareirailsang ar imwintihti kan koaros. Eri, kadehdepen me KAUN-O ketin pilkomwidahr pwe komwi en kin kakaun sapwellime aramas akan, iei met:
\v 2 Ni omwi pahn mweselsang rehi rahnwet, komwi pahn tuhwong ohl riemen limwahn sousoun Resel nan Selsa, nan sapwen Pensamin. Re pahn ndahng komwi me ahs ako me komw raparapahki dierekier, eri, omwi pahpao solahr pwunodki ahs ako, ahpw e uhd pwunupwunodkin komwi, oh kin idihdek, ‘Dahme I pahn wia pwehki nei pwutako?’
\v 3 Komwi ahpw pahn douluhlsang wasao, douluhlwohng ni tuhke sarawio me mi Tapor, wasao ke pahn tuhwong ohl silimen me kohkowohng wia ar meirong ong Koht nan Pedel. Eri, emen irail kahkahre kuht pwulopwul silimen, emen weuwa lopwon en pilawa siluh, a emen ehd kilin mahn me diren wain.
\v 4 Re pahn rahnmwahwih komwi oh kisekisehkin komwi riau lopwon en pilawa ko; eri, komw pahn ketiki.
\v 5 Mwuhr, komw pahn ketiwei nin Dohlen Koht me mi Kipea, wasa me kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia mi ie. Eri, ni ewen kelen kahnimwo, komw pahn tuhwong pwihnen soukohp ehu me kohkohdo sang ni pei sarawi ni dohlo, kesekesengki neirail arp, aip, keseng pepeuk, oh neirail lair kan. Re pahn kahkahlek oh wie weriwer.
\v 6 Ngenen Koht pahn ti pohmwi, eri, komw pahn iangirailda kahkahlek oh weriwer, oh komw pahn rasehngala aramas tohrohr emen.
\v 7 Ni mepwukat eh pahn pweida, komw pahn kapwaiada mehkoaros me Koht ketin audehkinkomwiher.
\v 8 Komw pahn tiengwei kowohng Kilkal, wasa I pahn tuhwong komwi ie oh wiahda meirong isihs ie oh meirong en kaminimin. Awih ie wasao rahn isuh, I lao kohwei oh padahkihong komwi dahme komw pahn ketin wia.”
\p 
\v 9 Eri, ni Sohl eh pirekekla sang rehn Samuel, Koht ahpw ketin wekidala Sohl unsek. Eri, mehkoaros me Samuel padahkihong, e pweida ni rahno.
\v 10 Ni Sohl oh eh laduwo ara lel Kipea, pwihnen soukohp ehu ahpw tuhwong ira. Ngenen Koht eri ti pohn Sohl, ih eri iangirailla kahkahlek oh weriwer.
\v 11 Aramas ako me ese ih mahs, ni ar kilangada eh wiewia soahng pwukat, re peidekpene, ndinda, “Dahme wiawihong nein Kis pwutaken? Ia duwe, Sohl wialahr soukohp emen?”
\v 12 A emen me kin kousoan wasao ahpw idekda, “A ia duwen meteikan—soukohp kei ar pahpa kan?” Iei wasa me tepin koasoi pwoatet kohsang ie, me kin koasoia, “Sohl wialahr soukohp emen?”\x - \xo 10:12 \xt 1 Sam 19.23-24.\x*
\v 13 Ni Sohl eh kaerala eh iang kahkahlek oh weriwer, e ahpw ketila ni pei sarawio pohn dohlo.
\p 
\v 14 Rien en Sohl eh pahpao eri idek reh, “Ke mihmihte ia?”
\p A Sohl ahpw sapeng, “I raparapahkihte ahs ako. Ni at sohte diar, se douluhlla tuhwong Samuel.”
\p 
\v 15 A rien eh pahpao pil idek, “A dahme e mahsanihong uhk?”
\p 
\v 16 Sohl eri sapeng, mahsanih, “E mahsanihong kiht me mahn ako dierekier.” Ahpw Sohl sohte ndaiong rien eh pahpao dahme Samuel ketihtihkihong duwen eh pahn nanmwarkihla.
\s1 Sohl ketin Ale Kawahupen Nanmwarki
\p 
\v 17 Samuel eri kapokonepene aramas akan nan Mispa ong ni sarawi ehu,
\v 18 eh ahpw padahkihong irail, “KAUN-O, Koht en Israel, ketin mahsanih, ‘I kahluwaikumwaildo sang Isip, oh doareikumwailla sang rehn mehn Isip kan oh sang rehn aramas teikan koaros me kin kalokei kumwail.
\v 19 Ngehi me amwail Koht, me kin doareikumwailsang amwail apwal oh lokolok koaros, ahpw rahnwet kumwail sohpeisangieier, oh kumwail pekidahr I en kihong kumwail emen nanmwarkien. Eri, me mwahu, kumwail pokonpene mwohn silangin KAUN-O nin duwen irekdien amwail kadaudok oh peneinei kan.’”
\p 
\v 20 Samuel eri kairakala ehuehu kadaudok, KAUN-O eri ketin pilada kadaudok en Pensamin.
\v 21 Samuel ahpw likwerihda kadaudok en Pensamin; eri, peneineien Matri ahpw pilipilda. Eri, ohl koaros nan peneineien Matri ahpw kohdahla, eri, Sohl, nein Kis, ahpw pilipilda. Irail rapahkiseli Sohl, re ahpw sohte diar.
\v 22 Eri, re ahpw pwurehng idek rehn KAUN-O, patohwan, “Pil mie emen tohrohr?”
\p KAUN-O eri sapeng, mahsanih, “Ien Sohl, e wie rukuruk nanpwungen kepwe kan.”
\p 
\v 23 Irail eri tangala oh kahrehdo Sohl rehn aramas ako. Eri, ni eh kesihnenda nanpwungarail, e sikdahsang irail koaros piht ehu.
\v 24 Samuel eri padahkihong aramas ako, “Iet ohl me KAUN-O ketin piladahr! Sohte emen rehtail me duwehte ih.”
\p Aramas ako koaros eri werkihda, “At nanmwarki en ketin mour werei!”
\p 
\v 25 Samuel eri kawehwehiong pokono duwen pwuhng oh duwen pwukoa kan en nanmwarki, oh ntingihedi ong nan pwuhk ehu oh kihdiong nan wasa sarawi ehu. Mwuhr, e ahpw kadarpeseng pokono ong ni imwarail kan.
\v 26 Sohl pil iang pwurala ni imweo me mi Kipea. Ekei aramas dengngan me Koht ketin kamwekidada kapehdirail ahpw iangala Sohl.
\v 27 A ekei me nan kapehd mwersuwed nda, “Ia duwen lahp menet e kak doareikitailla?” Re kailongkihla Sohl oh sohte men sewesehki mehkot.
\c 11
\s1 Sohl Kalowehdi mehn Ammon
\p 
\v 1 Mwurin sounpwong ehu, nanmwarki Nahas, mehn Ammon, kamwakidalahng nah karis kan nan kahnimw Sapes, nan sapwen Kilead oh kapilpene kahnimwo. Ohlen Sapes ko ndaiong Nahas, “Komw ketin wiahda ehu inowen nanpwungen kiht oh komwi, se ahpw pahn wiahkinkomwihla at kaun.”
\p 
\v 2 Nahas eri sapeng, “I pahn wiahda ehu inou nanpwungatail, ma I pahn pwadikasang palimaun en pwoaren mesen emenemen kumwail koaros, oh wiahkihla met kanamenekpen Israel pwon.”
\p 
\v 3 Kaunen Sapes ko ahpw nda, “Komw ketin mweidohng kiht mahs rahn isuh pwe se en kadarpeseng nait meninkeder kan nan wehin Israel. Ma sohte me pahn sewesei kiht, eri, se pahn uhpahiong komwi.”
\p 
\v 4 Meninkeder ko eri lel Kipea, wasa Sohl kin koukousoan ie. Eri, ni ar pakairkihda rohng pwoatet, aramas akan tapihada sengisengki ar nsensuwed.
\v 5 Sohl ahpwtehn kohkohdo sang nansapw ni ahnsowo, kahre nah kou. E ahpw keinemwe, “Dahkot mwo? Dahme aramas akan sengisengki?” Re ahpw padahkihong pakairo me meninkeder ko sang Sapes pakairkihdo.
\v 6 Ni Sohl eh rongada met, ngenen Koht ahpw ti powe, e ahpw engiengkihda kowahalp.
\v 7 E ahpw pelepeseng kou riemeno, oh kihong meninkeder kei pwe re en waseli kisehn kou ko nan wehin Israel oh pakairkihong aramas koaros, ketihtihki, “Ih pahn duwen kou koaros me nein irail koaros me sohte pahn idawehn Sohl oh Samuel kolahng nan mahwen.”
\p Eri, mehn Israel koaros ahpw lemmwikihda kupwur en KAUN-O. Irail koaros eri pokonpene ni lamalamtehpwoat.
\v 8 Sohl ahpw kapokoneirailpene nan Pesek: me 300,000 sang Israel, oh me 30,000 sang Suda.
\v 9 Irail eri ndaiong meninkeder en Sapes ko, “Kumwail kohwei ndaiong tohn Sapes ko me mwohn souwas en lakapw kumwail pahn kepitipitla.” Mehn Sapes ko ahpw inenen perenkihda ar rong pakair wet.
\v 10 Irail eri ndaiong Nahas, “Lakapw se pahn uhpah komwi, oh komw kak wiahiong kiht dahme komw kupwurki.”
\p 
\v 11 Mandahn rahno Sohl eri nehkpeseng nah aramas ako ong ni pwihn siluh, oh nin sohrahnie e ahpw kadarirailla pwe re en mahweniong mehn Ammon nan arail impwal kan. Re kemekemehla aramas lao lel nin souwas. Me luhwehdi ko ahpw tangpeseng.
\p 
\v 12 Mehn Israel ko eri ndaiong Samuel, “Ia irail ko me kakahski dene Sohl sohte pahn wia at nanmwarki? Komw ketikihong kiht pwe se en kemeirailla.”
\p 
\v 13 A Sohl ahpw mahsanih, “Sohte emen pahn kamakamala rahnwet, pwe iei rahnwet rahn me KAUN-O ketin kapitala Israel.”
\v 14 Samuel mahsanihong irail, “Kitail koaros pahn kohla Kilkal, oh iei wasao me kitail pahn pwurehng kasapwilada Sohl pwe en wia atail nanmwarki.”
\v 15 Irail koaros eri kohla Kilkal ni wasa sarawio, oh kasapwilada Sohl nan pokon sansal pwehn wiahla arail nanmwarki. Re ahpw pil wiahda ar meirong en kaminimin. Eri, Sohl oh mehn Israel koaros ahpw wiahda kasarawi wet.
\c 12
\s1 En Samuel eh Mahsen en Kamwurimwur
\p 
\v 1 Samuel eri mahsanihong mehn Israel ko, “Eri, I kapwaiadahr dahme kumwail peki rehi. I kihong kumwail nanmwarki men pwe en kaunkumwailda.
\v 2 Eri, e kaukaweidkumwailehr. A duwen ngehi, I ohl laudlahr oh moangepwetalahr, oh nei pwutak ko mihmi rehmwail. I wia sounkaweidpamwail sang ni ei mwahnakapw.
\v 3 Eri, iet ngehi. Ma mie sapwung ehu me I wiadahr, a kumwail kasaledohng ie mwohn silangin KAUN-O oh nanmwarki menet me e ketin piladahr. Mie emen kumwail me I kihsang nah kou de nah ahs? Mie me I pitihdi de kahpwalihala? Mie kisakis laud ehu me I alesang rehn emen kumwail? Ma mie mehkot sang nanpwungen me pwukat me I wiadahr, I pahn kapwungala oh kasapahlewei.”\x - \xo 12:3 \xt Sir 46.19.\x*
\p 
\v 4 Mehn Israel ko eri sapeng, “Komw sohte pitihkitedi de kahpwalihala emen kiht. Komw sohte pil ketikihsang kiht mehkot.”
\p 
\v 5 Samuel ahpw sapeng irail, ketihtihki, “KAUN-O oh nanmwarki me e ketin piladahret, ira me wia sounkadehde rahnwet duwen eh sohte dipei mwohmwail.”
\p Irail eri sapeng, nda, “Ei, KAUN-O me at sounkadehde.”
\p 
\v 6 Samuel eri pil ketihtihki, “KAUN-O iei ih me ketin pilada Moses oh Aaron, oh ketin kahluwahdo amwail pahpa kahlap ako sang Isip.\x - \xo 12:6 \xt Eks. 6.26.\x*
\v 7 Eri met, kumwail nennenla mahs, pwe I en wehkada mwohn silangin KAUN-O oh katamankinkumwailda manaman lapalap akan me KAUN-O ketin wiahda ni eh ketin doareikumwailla iangahki amwail pahpa kahlap ako.
\v 8 Kumwail tamanda ahnsou me Seikop oh eh peneinei lellahng Isip, oh duwen mehn Isip ko ar kalokeirail, oh duwen amwail pahpa kahlap ako ar likweriong KAUN-O oh peki sawas, eh ahpw ketin poaronehla Moses oh Aaron pwe en kahluwairail sang Isip oh koasoaneiraildi nan sahpwet.\x - \xo 12:8 \xt Eks. 2.23.\x*
\v 9 A irail ahpw manokehla KAUN-O, ar Koht, ih eri ketin mweidohng mehn Pilisdia kan, oh nanmwakien Mohap, oh Sisera, kaun lapalap en sounpeien kahnimw Asor, re en mahweniong irail oh kaloweiraildi.\x - \xo 12:9 \xt S.K 4.2; b S.K 13.1; c S.K 3.12.\x*
\v 10 Irail ahpw likweriong KAUN-O oh peki sawas, ketihtihki, ‘Maing KAUN, se patohwan dipadahr, pwehki at sohpeisang komwi oh kaudokiong Paal akan oh Asdarde. Komw ketin kapitkitasang rehn at imwintihti kan, se ahpw pahn kaudokiong komwi!’\x - \xo 12:10 \xt S.K 10.10-15.\x*
\v 11 KAUN-O eri ketin poaronehdo Kidion, mwuri Parak, mwuri Sepda, oh ngehi me keieu mwuhr, pwe se en kapitkumwailsang rehn amwail imwintihti kan. Kumwail eri momourier ni meleilei.\x - \xo 12:11 \xt S.K 7.1; b S.K 4.6; c S.K 11.29; d 1 Sam. 3.20.\x*
\v 12 Oh ni amwail kilang nanmwarki Nahas, mehn Ammono, me pahn mahweniong kumwail, kumwail ahpw sohpeisang KAUN-O, amwail nanmwarki oh ndaiong ie, ‘Se mwahuki emen nanmwarki tohrohr en kaunkitada.’\x - \xo 12:12 \xt 1 Sam. 8.19.\x*
\p 
\v 13 “Eri iet nanmwarki me kumwail piladahro; kumwail me pekihda, eri iet ih KAUN-O ketikihongkumwailehr.
\v 14 Mehkoaros pahn pweida mwahu, ma kumwail pahn wauneki KAUN-O, amwail Koht, papah ih, rong oh kapwaiada sapwellime mahsen kan, oh ma kumwail oh amwail nanmwarkio pahn idawehn ih.
\v 15 Ahpw ma kumwail sohte pahn men rong KAUN-O, oh kapwaiada sapwellime mahsen kan, e pahn ketin uhwong kumwail oh amwail nanmwarki.
\v 16 Eri, kumwail nennenla, pwe kumwail pahn kilang manaman lapalap me KAUN-O pahn ketin wiahda.
\v 17 Eri, ahnsou wet, iei ahnsou me keteu sohte kin mweredi? Eri, I pahn kapakap pwe KAUN-O en ketin kadaridi nahnsapwe oh keteu. Ni ahnsou me met pahn pweida, kumwail pahn pehmada uwen lauden dihp me kumwail wiahiong KAUN-O ni amwail peki emen nanmwarki.”
\p 
\v 18 Samuel eri kapakap, oh ni rahnohte KAUN-O ahpw ketin kadaridi nahnsapwe oh keteu. Aramas ako koaros ahpw masakada KAUN-O oh Samuel,
\v 19 re ahpw ndaiong Samuel, “Maing, komw kasakaskin kiht rehn KAUN-O, omwi Koht, pwe se dehr mehla. Met se eseier me se pil kapataiong dipat teikan dipen at pekihda nanmwarki men.”
\p 
\v 20 Samuel eri sapeng irail, nda, “Kumwail dehr masak. Mehnda ma kumwail wiadahr soangen suwed laud wet, ahpw kumwail dehpa sohpeisang KAUN-O, kumwail uhpaiong ni mohngiong unsek.
\v 21 Kumwail dehr idawehn koht likamw akan; pwe re sohte kak sewesei kumwail de doareikumwailla, pwe soangen koht pwukat me mwahl oh so-kateparail.
\v 22 A Koht ketin kahukihla me e sohte pahn ketin keseikumwailla, pwe e ketin kupwuredahr en wiahkinkumwailla sapwellime aramas.
\v 23 A duwen ngehi, Koht ketin koasoanehdi me I pahn wiahda dihp ma I tokedihsang kapakapkin kumwail. Ahpw I pahn kin padahkihong kumwail dahme mwahu oh pwung ahnsou koaros.
\v 24 Kumwail peikiong KAUN-O oh uhpaiong ni loalopwoat oh mohngiong unsek. Kumwail tamataman manaman lapalap akan me e ketin wiahda pwehki kumwail.
\v 25 Ahpw ma kumwail pahn wonlahte nan dipamwail kan, kumwail oh amwail nanmwarki pahn mwomwla.”
\c 13
\s1 Mahwen Ong men Pilisdia kan
\p 
\v 1 \f i \fr 13:1 \fk IRE TIKITIK EHU: \ft Ire tikitik wet ni mahsen en Ipru sohte nohn sansal wasa riau; “Sohl sounpar...ni eh wiahla nanmwarki, oh e kakaun Israel erein sounpar....”\f*
\v 2 Sohl ahpw ketin pilada mehn Israel 3,000, a meteiko koaros e kadaralahng ni imwarail. Me 2,000 mihmihte reh nan Mikmas oh nan sahpw nahnahn Pedel; a 1,000 iang nah pwutak Sonadan nan Kipea, nan sapwen kadaudok en Pensamin.
\p 
\v 3 Sonadan eri kemehla kaunen Pilisdia men nan Kepa, oh mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw rongada. Sohl ahpw kadarpeseng meninkeder kei pwe re en peuk sowi nansahpwo pwon oh kehsehki mehn Ipru ko re en onopadahng mahwen.
\v 4 Mehn Israel ko koaros rongada duwen Sohl eh kemehla kaunen Pilisdiao, oh duwen mehn Pilisdia ko ar kin mwamwahlikin irail. Aramas koaros eri iang pokonla rehn Sohl nan Kilkal.
\p 
\v 5 Mehn Pilisdia ko pil pokonpene pwe re en mahweniong mehn Israel ko. Mie rehn mehn Pilisdia ko werennansapw 30,000, soundake oahs 6,000, oh sounpei inenen tohto, rasehng pihken ni oaroahr akan. Re kohla Mikmas, palimesehn Pedapen; re ahpw kauwada ie imwarail impwal kan.
\v 6 Re mahweniong mehn Israel ko oh kahrehiong mehn Israel nan apwal mehlel. Ekei irail eri rukula nan pwoaren paip akan oh nan pwoahr akan, nanpwungen takai oh nan pwarer madekeng kan oh nan warawar akan.
\v 7 Ekei kotehla Pillap Sordan sipallahng nan sapwen Kad oh Kilead.
\p Sohl ahpw ketikette Kilkal, oh aramas akan me iang ih rerrerki ar masepwehk.
\v 8 Sohl awiawiheki Samuel erein rahn isuh, duwen me Samuel padahkihong. Samuel ahpw sohte pwarodo Kilkal. Aramas akan eri tapihada kohkohla sang rehn Sohl.\x - \xo 13:8 \xt 1 Sam. 10.8\x*
\v 9 Ih eri mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail wadohng ie meirong isihs kan oh meirong en kaminimin kan.” Sohl eri wiahda meirong isihso;
\v 10 oh ni eh ketin kaerala meirongo, Samuel ahpw lel wasao. Sohl eri ketila tuhwong oh kasamwo,
\v 11 a Samuel ahpw patohwanohng, “Dahme komw ketin wiadahren?”
\p Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “I kilangehr duwen aramas akan ar kohkohpeseng, oh komw sohte pwarodo ni ahnsou me komw kilelehdi. I pil kilangehr duwen mehn Pilisdia kan ar pokonpenehr nan Mikmas.
\v 12 Eri, I lemeiong me mehn Pilisdia kan pahn mahweniong ie wasaht, nan Kilkal, ahpw I saikinte wia mehkot pwe Koht en kupwuramwahwih ie. Ihme I wiakihda meirong wet.”
\p 
\v 13 Samuel ahpw sapeng, patohwanohng, “Tiahk en kupwuropwon ehu me komw ketin wiadahr. Komw sohte kapwaiada mahsen en KAUN-O, omwi Koht me e ketin koasoanehdiong komwi. Ma komw kapwaiada, e pahn ketin mweidohng komwi oh kadaudokomwi kan re en kaunda Israel kohkohlahte.
\v 14 Eri, omwi mwehi sohte pahn werei. Pwehki omwi sapeikiong KAUN-O, e pahn ketin rapahkihda ohl emen me e ketin kupwurki, oh e pahn ketin kasapwilada pwe en kaunda sapwellime aramas akan.” \x - \xo 13:14 \xt Wie. 13.22.\x*
\p 
\v 15 Samuel eri mwesella sang Kilkal. A aramas teiko ahpw idawehnla Sohl ni eh ketiketla rehn sapwellime sounpei ko. Irail ketila sang Kilkal ketilahng Kipea nan sapwen Pensamin. Sohl eri kasawih sapwellime sounpei ko, irail me 600.
\v 16 Sohl, sapwellime pwutak Sonadan, oh neira sounpei ko eri mihmihte Kepa, nan sapwen Pensamin. A mehn Pilisdia ko kauwada imwarail impwal ko nan Mikmas.
\v 17 Mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw kin kohpeseng pwe en pirapa soahng kan ni pwihn siluh: ehu pwihn kin kolahng Opra, nan sapwen Sual:
\v 18 ehu pwihn kin kolahng Ped Oron; oh ehu pwihn kin kolahng ni irepen sahpw me sallahng Wahun Sepoim oh nan sapwtehno.
\p 
\v 19 Sohte sounsukmete emen kak dierekda nan Israel, pwe mehn Pilisdia ko sohte mweidohng mehn Ipru kan en wiahda neirail kedlahs oh ketieu.
\v 20 (Mehn Israel ko uhdahn pahn kohla rehn mehn Pilisdia ko pwehn ede neirail mehn deipwel kan, neirail kuha kan, neirail sile kan, oh neirail naip akan.
\v 21 A pweinen adahd en sile oh naip mwohni silper ehu, a pweinen adahd en mehn deipwel kan oh kuha, mwohni silper riau.)
\v 22 Eri, ihme ni rahnen mahweno sohte sounpeien Israel men me wa kedlahs de ketieu, ihte Sohl kelehpw oh sapwellime pwutak Sonadan.
\p 
\v 23 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri kadarala pwihnen sounpei ehu pwe re en sinsile wasahn kot en Mikmas.
\c 14
\s1 En Sonadan eh Doadoahk Kommwad nan Mahwen
\p 
\v 1 Rahn ehu Sonadan ahpw ndaiong mwahnakapw me kin wa nah dipwisoun mahwen ko, “Kita kohla mahs nan kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia kan.” Ahpw e sohte mwahn ndaiong eh pahpao.
\v 2 Sohl ketiket nan kahnimpwalo pahn tuhke pwohmakraneid pwoat nan Mikron, me sohte dohsang Kipea; oh sounpei 600 me iangih.
\v 3 (Samworo me likawih likou ihpod \f j \fr 14:3 \fk IHPOD: \ft Tehk ni kawehwehpen lepin mahsen kan.\f* iei Ahisa, nein Ahidup rien Ikapod, nein Pineas, me pahpa kahlapki Ilai, samworoun KAUN-O nan Sailo.) Eri, aramas ako sohte ese me Sonadan kohkohla sang rehrail.
\p 
\v 4 Eri, ni Wasahn Kot en Mikmas, wasa me Sonadan pahn kotehla, kolahng nan kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia ko, takai kalaimwun kengkeng riau mi wasahn koto, ehu mi apali ahlo, a ehu apali. Eri, ehu adaneki Poses, a ehu adaneki Sene.
\v 5 Ehu takaio mi paliepeng en wasahn koto, sallahng Mikmas, a ehu palieir, sallahng Kepa.
\p 
\v 6 Sonadan eri ndaiong mwahnakapwo, “Kita kohla mahs nan kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia rotorot akan. Mweinele KAUN-O pahn ketin sewesei kita; ma iei, eri e pahn ketin kupwure pwe kitail en powehdi, mehnda ma kitail me malaulau.”
\p 
\v 7 Mwahnakapwo ahpw sapeng, nda, “Kupwuromwien en pweida. I pahn ieiang komwihte.”
\p 
\v 8 Sonadan eri nda, “Me mwahu! Kita kohla oh pwarohng irail.
\v 9 Ma irail pahn nda kita en awih pwe irail pahn kohdo rehta, eri, kita pahn awih irail.
\v 10 Ahpw ma re nda kita en kohla rehrail, eri, kita pahn kohla, pwe iei met kilel en kupwuren KAUN-O, kitail en poweiraildi.”
\p 
\v 11 Ni mehn Pilisdia ko ar kilangirahda, re ahpw nda, “Ien ekei mehn Ipru me apwtehn pwarada sang nan pwoaren paip akan, wasa re kin rukuruk ie.”
\v 12 Sounpeien Pilisdia ko eri likweri Sonadan oh mwahnakapwo, ketihtihki, “Kumwa kohdahdo mahs met, pwe mie mehkot se pahn ndaiong kumwa.”
\p Sonadan eri ndaiong mwahnakapwo, “Nna kita! KAUN-O ketin kupwuredahr Israel en poweiraildi.”
\v 13 Sonadan eri kerepdahla wasahn koto, a mwahnakapwo idawehnla. Sonadan eri peiong mehn Pilisdia ko oh kesepwekeiraildi, a mwahnakapwo ahpw kemeirailla.
\v 14 Ni keieun mahwen wet, Sonadan oh mwahnakapwo kemehla kereniong ohl riehk nan kisin wasa tikitik kis.
\v 15 Mehn Pilisdia koaros nan mohso, oh nan kahnimpwalo, ahpw masepwehkada kowahlap, iangahki pwihnen sounpei me kin kohieilahng pirap. Sahpwo ahpw rerada, oh lemmw ehu ahpw kipehdi aramas koaros.
\s1 Lohdien mehn Pilisdia ko
\p 
\v 16 Sapwellimen Sohl sounsilasil ko nan Kipea, nan sapwen Pensamin ahpw kilangada mehn Pilisdia ko ar pingida oh tangatangseli.
\v 17 Sohl eri mahsanihong sapwellime sounpei ko, “Kumwail wadek sounpei kan oh kilang ihs me sohte mie.” Irail eri wadek sounpei ko, oh diarada me Sonadan, oh nah mwahnakapwo me kin wa nah dipwisoun mahwen ko, me sohte mie.
\v 18 Sohl eri mahsanihong samworo Ahisa, “Komw ketikihdo likou ihpodo met.” (Pwe ni rahno Ahisa wa likowo tiengki mwohn mehn Israel ko.)
\v 19 Nindokon Sohl eh mahmahseniong samworo, pingiping en mehn Pilisdia ko wie lalaudlahte nan arail kahnimpwalo. Sohl eri mahsanihong samworo, “Solahr ahnsou en rapahki kupwur en KAUN-O duwen mwekid wet!”
\v 20 Eri, Sohl oh sapwellime ko ahpw mwekidlahng wasahn mahweno rehn mehn Pilisdia ko, me pingidahr kowahlap oh pepeipene nanpwungarail.
\v 21 Mehn Ipru ko me iangala mehn Pilisdia ko rahn ekei mwowe, oh me mihmi rehrail nan ar kahnimpwalo, uhdahte pwurodohng rehn mehn Israel ko oh iangala Sohl oh Sonadan.
\v 22 A mehn Israel ko me wie rukuruk nan sahpw nahnahn Epraim, re pil rongada duwen mehn Pilisdia ko ar tangpeseng, irail eri pil iangala pwakih mehn Pilisdia ko,
\v 23 re pepeiong irail lao daulihala Pedapen. KAUN-O eri ketin kapitala mehn Israel ko rahno.
\s1 Mwekid kan Mwurin Mahweno
\p 
\v 24 Mehn Israel ko inenen luwetala pwehki ar duhpekla rahno, pwe Sohl wiahda inou ehu oh kahula, mahsanih, “Rahnwet, ma mehmen pahn tungoale mehkot mwohn ei pahn dupuk en ei imwintiht kan ar suwed ong ie, a en riahla.” Eri, sohte emen me tungoale mehkot rahno pwon.
\v 25 Irail koaros ahpw lellahng nan wel ehu oh diarada sukehn loangalap tohto.
\v 26 Wasao inenen diren sukehn loangalap, ahpw sohte me tungoale, pwehki ar masak keriahn Sohl.
\v 27 Ahpw Sonadan sohte iang rong keria me eh pahpao wiahiong aramas akan. Ih eri alehte nah sokono, diehki nan sukehn loangalapo oh kangala. Ni ahnsowohte e kehlailada.
\v 28 Emen ohl ako ahpw ndahng, “Kitail koaros mehkilahr atail men mwenge, a omw pahpao ahpw kihong kitail keria wet, mahsanih, ‘Mehmen me pahn tungoale mehkot rahnwet en riahla.’”
\p 
\v 29 Sonadan eri sapeng, ketihtihki, “Ei pahpao wiahiong aramas akan tiahk sakanakan ehu. Kumwail kilang duwen ei kehlailadahr pwehki ei tungoale sukehn loangalapo.
\v 30 Meid pahn mwahu ong aramas akan rahnwet, ma re tungoale kisin tungoal ko me re koledi sang ar imwintiht ko ni ahnsou me re kaloweiraildi. Ia uwen tohtohn mehn Pilisdia me reh pahn kak kemehla!”
\p 
\v 31 Eri, rahno mehn Israel ko ahpw kalowehdi mehn Pilisdia ko sang Mikmas lelohng Aisalon. Mehn Israel ko inenen luwetkihla ar duhpekla,
\v 32 ihme re tangalahngete ni dipwisou me re adihasang rehn arail imwintihti ko, oh alehte sihpw oh kou kan oh kemeirailla wasao oh kangala uduk oh iangahki nta.
\v 33 Pakair ahpw kohieng Sohl, me patohwan, “Komw mwahngih pwe aramas akan dipadahr ong KAUN-O ni ar kangadahr uduk me mie nta.”\x - \xo 14:33 \xt Sen. 9.4; Lip 7.26-27; 17.10-14; 19.26; Deud. 12.16,23; 15.23.\x*
\p Sohl eri kapitie laudida, mahsanih, “Kumwail sapwungalahr! Kumwail katapwurehdo wasaht ehu takai lauden.”
\v 34 E ahpw wiahda ehu koasoandi: “Kumwail kohwei rehn aramas koaros oh padahkihong irail re en wahdo wasaht neirail kou kan oh sihpw kan. Pwe re uhdahn pahn kemehla oh kang wasaht, iei duwen me re sohte pahn dipkihda ong KAUN-O ni ar pahn tungoale uduk iangahki nta.” Eri, nipwongohte, irail koaros ahpw wapene neirail kou ko oh kemehla wasao.
\v 35 Sohl eri kauwada ehu pei sarawi ong KAUN-O wasao. Iei keieun pei sarawi me e ketin kauwada.
\p 
\v 36 Sohl eri mahsanihong sapwellime sounpei ko, “Kitail kohdihla oh mahweniong mehn Pilisdia ko pwohnget oh kauweirailla oh kemeirailla koaros.”
\p Irail ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Komw ketin wiahda duwen kupwuromwien.” A samworo ahpw patohwan, “Kitail patohwan rapahki mahs kupwur en Koht.”
\p 
\v 37 Sohl eri kalelapak rehn Koht, patohwan, “Maing, ia duwe? I en wonlahte mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan? Komw pahn ketin kupwurei kiht pwe se en kaloweiraildi?” Koht ahpw sohte ketin sapeng rahno.
\v 38 Sohl eri mahsanihong kaunen aramas akan, “Kumwail pokonpene wasaht oh kalelapak soangen sapwung da me wiawidahr rahnwet.
\v 39 Pwe I inoukihda ni mwaren KAUN-O me ieias, Sounkomour en Israel, mehnda ma nei pwutak Sondadan me dipadahr, a e pahn kamakamala.” Eri, irail ahpw nennenlahte, sohte sapeng.
\v 40 Sohl eri mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail koaros kesihnenda wasahn, a ngehi oh Soandan pahn mi wasaht.”
\p Irail eri sapeng, patohwan, “Komw ketin wiahda kupwuromwien.”
\p 
\v 41 Sohl ahpw patohwanohng KAUN-O, “Maing KAUN, dahme komwi sohte ketin sapengkin ie rahnwet? Maing KAUN, Koht en Israel, komw ketin kasaledohng kiht kupwuromwien sang ni takai sarawi pwukat. Ma dihp wet iei en Sonadan de pein dipei, a komw ketin kasalehda ni takai Urim; a ma dipen sapwellimomwi aramas en Israel kan, a komw ketin kasalehda ni takai Dumim.”\f k \fr 14:41 \fk URIM...DUMIM: \ft Samworo kan kin doadoahngki kisin takai riau wet pwehn rapahki kupwur en Koht; e sohte nohn dehde ia mwomwen ar kin doadoahngki.\f* Pasapengo eri kasalehda me Sonadan oh Sohl me dipadahr. Aramas ako eri kasaledekla.\x - \xo 14:41 \xt Nemp 27.21; 1 Sam. 28.6.\x*
\v 42 Sohl eri mahsanih, “Pilada ihs rehn ngehi oh nei pwutak Sonadan.” Sonadan eri pilipilda.
\v 43 Sohl eri idekda rehn Sonadan, “Dahme ke wiahda?”
\p Sonadan eri sapeng, patohwan, “I tungoalehda kisin sukehn loangalap kis. Eri, iet ngehi—ngehi me pahn mehla.”
\p 
\v 44 Sohl ahpw mahsanihong, “Koht en ketin kemeiehla ma ke sohte pahn kamakamala!”
\p 
\v 45 A aramas ako ahpw patohwanohng Sohl, “Ia duwe, Sonadan pahn kamakamala, nan ih me powehdi en mehn Israel ar imwintihti kan? Met sohte kak! Se kahukihla ni mwaren Koht ieias me sohte apwoat pitenmoange pahn pwupwusang. Me e wiadahr rahnwet, sang ni sawas en Koht.” Aramas ako eri doarehla Sonadan sang mehla.
\p 
\v 46 Mwurin mwo, Sohl ahpw sohla pwakih mehn Pilisdia ko, re ahpw pwurala nan uhdahn sapwarailo.
\s1 Mwehin Nanmwarki Sohl oh Sapwellime Peneinei
\p 
\v 47 Mwurin Sohl eh wiahla nanmwarkien Israel, e ketin mahweniong imwintihti kan wasa koaros: mehn Mohap, mehn Ammon, oh mehn Edom, nanmwarkien Sopa, oh pil Pilisdia kan. E kin powehdi wasa koaros me e kin mahwen ie.
\v 48 E pil wia lapalahn mahwen ehu ong mehn Amalek oh pil kaloweiraildi. E ketin doarehla mehn Israel sang ar imwintihti kan koaros.
\p 
\v 49 Eri, iet sapwellimen Sohl pwutak kan: Sonadan, Ispi, oh Malkisuha. Eden sapwellime serepein laudo, iei Merap, oh me tikitiko, Maikal.
\v 50 Mwaren sapwellime likend, Ahinoam, nein Ahimas; mwaren sapwellime kaun lapalap en sounpei, iei Apner, nein Ner, rien eh pahpao.
\v 51 Eri, Kis en Sohl eh pahpa, oh Ner, en Apner eh pahpa, iei ira nein Apiel.
\v 52 Eri, erein Sohl eh ieias e kin ketin mahmahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan. Ahnsou koaros me e kin diar ohl emen me kehlail a e kin kilelehdi pwe en iangala sapwellime sounpei kan.
\c 15
\s1 Mahwen Ong mehn Amalek
\p 
\v 1 Samuel eri padahkihong Sohl, “Ih ngehi me KAUN-O ketin poaronehdo pwe I en keieikomwihdi pwe komwi en wiahla nanmwarkien sapwellime aramas en Israel. Eri, komw karonge dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap, ketin mahsanih.\x - \xo 15:1 \xt 1 Sam. 10.1.\x*
\v 2 E pahn ketin kaloke mehn Amalek kan pwehki ar pelianda mehn Israel kan ni ar kohkohdo sang Isip.\x - \xo 15:2 \xt Eks. 17.8-14; Deud. 25.17-19.\x*
\v 3 Eri, kohwei oh mahweniong irail oh kamwomwala douluhl mehkoaros me mie rehrail. Sohte mehkot pahn luhwehdi: ohl akan, lih akan, seri kan, me pwelel kan, kou oh sihpw kan, kamel oh ahs akan, koaros pahn kamakamala.”
\p 
\v 4 Sohl eri kapokonepene sapwellime karis en sounpei kan oh ketin kasawih irail nan Telem: irail me 200,000 sang Israel oh 10,000 sang Suda.
\v 5 Ih oh sapwellime sounpei ko ahpw kolahng Amalek, oh awihiraildi nan pillap madada pwoat.
\v 6 E ahpw kehkehlingkihong mehn Ken kan, mahsanih, “Kumwail kohwei oh tohrohreweisang mehn Amalek kan, pwe kumwail en dehr iang irail kamakamala. Pwe kumwail inenen kadek ong mehn Israel kan ni ar kohdo sang Isip.” Mehn Ken ko eri kohkohla sang rehn mehn Amalek ko.
\p 
\v 7 Sohl eri kalowehdi mehn Amalek ko sang Apila lellahng Sur, palimesehn Isip.
\v 8 E ahpw koledi Akak, nanmwarkien Amalek, ahpw e sohte kamakamala. A aramas teikan koaros kamakamala.
\v 9 Eri, Sohl oh sapwellime ko sohte kemehla Akak, oh pil sohte kemehla sihpw me keieu mwahu, oh kou, oh koupwul, oh sihmpwul, oh mehkot me keieu kaselel. Ahpw mehkoaros me sohte kesempwal de katepe, re kamwomwala.
\s1 Koht ketin Soikala Sohl sang eh Nanmwarki
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong Samuel,
\v 11 “I koluhkilahr ei kasapwilada Sohl nanmwarki; pwe e sohpeiseng ie oh solahr kin kapwaiada ei kosonned akan.” Samuel eri nsensuwedkihla kowahlap, oh nipwongo pwon e wie ngidingidkihong KAUN-O eh pekipek.
\v 12 Mandahn rahno, nimensehngie, e ahpw ketila rapahki Sohl. E ahpw rongada me Sohl samwalahngehr kahnimw Karmel, wasa e kauwada ie mehn kataman ehu ong pein ih; oh mwuhr, e ahpw kohkohla Kilkal.
\v 13 Samuel eri lella reh. Sohl ahpw rahnmwahwih, mahsanih, “KAUN-O en ketin kupwuramwahwih komwi, Samuel! I kapwaiadahr sapwellimen KAUN-O mahsen kan.”
\p 
\v 14 Samuel eri patohwan idek, “A dahme I rongorongki ngilen kou oh ngilen sihpw?”
\p 
\v 15 Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “Nei sounpei kat me kihsang rehn mehn Amalek ko. Re katohrehla me keieu mwahu rehn sihpw kan oh kou kan mehn wia meirong ong KAUN-O, omw Koht. A meteiko koaros se kamwomwala douluhl.”\f l \fr 15:15 \fk KAMWOMWALA DOULUHL: \ft Mahn pwukat kasarawihongehr KAUN-O, oh e pahn kamwomwmwomwla douluhl (tehk Lip 27.28).\f*
\p 
\v 16 Samuel ahpw patohwanohng, “Erier! Met I pahn kasalehiong komwi dahme KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie pwohng.”
\p Sohl ahpw sapeng, “Komw mahsanihodo.”
\p 
\v 17 Samuel eri patohwan, “Sohl, mehnda ma komwi wiahkin komwi aramas tikitik, ahpw komwi me kaunen kadaudok kan en Israel. KAUN-O ketin keieikomwihdi nanmwarkien Israel,
\v 18 oh ketin poaroneikomwihwei, oh mahsanih komwi en kamwomwala aramas suwed ko en Amalek. E mahsanih komwi en mahweniong irail, komw lao kameirailla koaros.
\v 19 Eri, dahme kahrehda komw sohte peikikihong? Dahme kahrehda komw noarohkekihda dipwisou ko, oh wiahkihda mehkot me uhwong kupwur en KAUN-O?”
\p 
\v 20 Sohl ahpw sapeng Samuel, mahsanih, “I peikiongehr KAUN-O. I patohla nin duwen me e mahsanih, oh patohwando Nanmwarki Akak, oh kemehla mehn Amalek koaros.
\v 21 A nei sounpei kan me sohte kemehla sihpw oh kou keieu mwahu kan me re koledi; pwe re wahdo wasaht nan Kilkal, mehn wia meirong ong KAUN-O, omwi Koht.”
\p 
\v 22 Samuel ahpw patohwan, “Mehnia tiahk me KAUN-O kin ketin kupwurperenki, rehn peik de kisakis oh meirong? Eri, peik me mwahusang mehlel meirongkihong sihpw me keieu kaselel kan.
\v 23 Kahngohdiong ih, iei mehkot suwed, duwehte dipen wunani; oh aklapalap ong ih, duwehte dipen pwongih dikedik en eni. Eri, pwehki omwi soikalahr mahsen en KAUN-O, e pil ketin soingkomwilahr sang omwi nanmwarki.”
\p 
\v 24 Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “I dipadahr, ni ei sohte kapwaiada mahsen en KAUN-O oh omwi kaweid kan. I masakada nei aramas akan oh mweidohng re en wia nsenarail.
\v 25 Eri met, I patohwan peki mahkpen dipeiet; oh komwi en iangiehda kohla Kilkal, pwe I en kak iang komwi kaudokiong KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 26 Samuel ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “I sohte pahn iang komwi pwurala. Komw soikalahr mahsen en KAUN-O oh e ketin soingkomwilahr sang omwi nanmwarkien Israel.”
\p 
\v 27 Samuel eri pirekekla pwe en kohkohla, a Sohl ahpw poaralahng eh likoun likio oh koledi, e ahpw tehrpeseng.\x - \xo 15:27 \xt 1 Sam. 28.17; 1 Nan. 11.30-31.\x*
\v 28 Samuel ahpw padahkihong Sohl, “KAUN-O ketin tehrasang komwi rahnwet wehin Israel oh ketikihong emen tohrohr me mwahusang komwi.
\v 29 Koht lapalp en Israel sohte kin ketin likamw de wekidala kupwure. Kaidehk ih aramas me kin wekidala eh lamalam.”
\p 
\v 30 Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “I dipadahr mehlel. A komw kihong wauwi mwohn mesen kaunen nei aramas akan oh pil mwohn mehn Israel koaros. Komw ketin iang ie pwurala pwe I en kak kaudokiong KAUN-O, omwi Koht.”
\v 31 Samuel eri iang pwurala Kilkal, Sohl ahpw kaudokiong KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 32 Samuel eri patohwan, “Kumwail kahrehdo mwohi Nanmwmarki Akak.” Akak eri pakahrla mwohn Samuel, wie rerrerki eh masepwehk oh mengimengloalki, “Ia uwen kansensuwed en ei pahn kamakamlaht!”
\v 33 Samuel eri patohwanohng, “Nin duwen sapwellimomwi kedlahs eh kahrehiong lih neitik tohto eh sohla nair seri, ih duwen met omwi nohno solahr pahn nah seri.” Ih eri alehte Akak, pelepeseng mwohn pei sarawien Kilkal.
\p 
\v 34 Samuel eri kohkohla Rama, oh Nanmwarki Sohl ahpw ketiketla Kipea.
\v 35 Samuel eri sohla pwurehng kilang Sohl erein eh mour; e ahpw kin wie nsensuwedki. KAUN-O ahpw ketin kupwur toutoukihla eh ketin kasapwilada Sohl en wia nanmwarkien Israel.
\c 16
\s1 Depit Keidiong en Nanmwarki
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong Samuel, “Ia erein omw pahn kin nsensuwedki Sohl? I soikasangehr en wia nanmwarkien Israel. Eri, wahda ekis kisin lehn olip en. Pwe I pahn kadaruhkowohng Pedleem, rehn ohl emen ede Sehsi, pwe I piladahr emen nah pwutak pwe en wiahla nanmwarki.”
\p 
\v 2 Samuel eri patohwan idek, “Ia duwen ei kak wie soahngen? Ma Sohl pahn rongada, e pahn kemeiehla.”
\p KAUN-O ahpw ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “Wahda emen koupwulen, ke ahpw nda me ke kohkolahng wia meirong ong KAUN-O.
\v 3 Ke ahpw luke Sehsi ong ni meirongo. Eri, I ahpw pahn ndaiong uhk dahme ke pahn wia. Ke pahn keiehdi ohl me I pahn pilada pwe en nanmwarki.”
\p 
\v 4 Samuel eri wiahda nin duwen me KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong. Ih eri patopatohla Pedleem, wasa me kaunen kahnimwo tuhwong ih ie, oh wie rerrerki ar masepwehk. Re ahpw idek, “Maing, komw ketikihdo popohl, de dah?”
\p 
\v 5 E ahpw sapeng irail, ketihtihki, “Ei, I wahdo meleilei. I kohdohn wia meirong ong KAUN-O. Kumwail kamwakeleikumwailda oh kohdo iang ie.” E pil padahkihong Sehsi oh nah pwutak ko re en kamwakelda; e ahpw pil lukeirailohng ni meirongo.
\p 
\v 6 Eri, ni ar lel wasao, Samuel ahpw kilangada nein Sehsi nah pwutak Eliap. E ahpw mengimengloalki, “Ohl menet me kesikesihnen mwohn silangin KAUN-O, ele iei ih ohl me e ketin piladahr.”
\p 
\v 7 A KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong Samuel, “Ke dehr tehk duwen eh reirei oh masamwahu. Pwe kaidehk ih me I piladahr. Pwehki I sohte kin kasawih aramas nin duwen me aramas akan kin wia. Aramas kin kasawih mwomwen aramas, ahpw ngehi, I kin kasawih nan mohngiong en aramas akan.”
\p 
\v 8 Sehsi ahpw ekerodo nah pwutak Apinadap oh kasalehiong Samuel. Samuel ahpw ketihtihki, “Soh! KAUN-O sohte ketin pilada ih.”
\v 9 Sehsi ahpw pil kasalehiong Samma. A Samuel pil ketihtihki, “Soh! Kaidehn ih me KAUN-O ketin pilada.”
\v 10 Ih duwen Sehsi eh kasalehiong Samuel nah pwutak isimeno. A Samuel ahpw ketihtihkihong, “Soh, kaidehk! KAUN-O sohte ketin pilada emen irail pwukat.”
\v 11 Samuel eri idek rehn Sehsi, “Ihte noumwi pwutak kan met, solahr pil emen?”
\p Sehsi ahpw sapeng, “Mie emen me keieu tikitik, ahpw e sohte iang mi met, pwe e sinsile nait sihpw kan.”
\p Samuel eri ketihtihki, “Komw ekerodo. Kitail sohte pahn wia atail meirong e lao leledo.”
\v 12 Sehsi eri ileklahng en kohdo. Mwahnakapw pwulopwul men ih, masamwahu, paliwaramwahu, oh mas pwukapwuk. KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong Samuel, “Iei ih met—keiehdi!”
\v 13 Samuel eri ale lehn olipo oh keiehdi Depit mwohn mesen rie ko. Ngenen KAUN-O eri ti pohn Depit oh ketin ieiang sang rahno kohla. Samuel eri pwurala Rama.
\s1 Depit nan Tehnpas en Sohl
\p 
\v 14 Ngenen KAUN-O ahpw ketieisang rehn Sohl; a ngehn suwed ehu me KAUN-O ketin kadarodo ahpw kaloke.
\v 15 Sapwellime papah ko eri patohwanohng, “Se patohwan ese me ngehn suwed sang ni mweimweien Koht me kapwunodeikomwidahr.
\v 16 Komw mahsanih pwe se en rapahkihdo emen ohlen me ese kesengki arp, pwe ni ngehn suwedo eh pahn kin ti pohmwi, ohl menet en kin kesengiong komwi. Komwi ahpw pahn kupwuramwahukihla.”
\p 
\v 17 Sohl eri mahsanih, “Nna, kumwail rapahkihda aramas emen me kadek keseng, oh kahrehdo rehi.”
\p 
\v 18 Eri, emen sapwellime papah ko ahpw patohwan, “Sehsi, mehn Pedleem, mie nah pwutak emen me inenen kadek keseng. Me pil ohl dengngang men, sounpei kommwad, kadek lokaia, oh paliwaramwahu. KAUN-O kin ketin ieiang.”
\p 
\v 19 Sohl eri poaronehla meninkeder kei rehn Sehsi, mahsanih, “Komw kadarodohng ie mahs noumwi pwutak Depit, silepen sihpw kan.”
\v 20 Sehsi eri kadarala Depit rehn Sohl, iangahkihla ehd kilin mahn me diren wain, kuht pwulopwul men, oh ahs emen me wa kiden pilawa.
\v 21 Depit eri kohla rehn Sohl oh tapiada papah. Sohl ahpw inenen poakepoakehla Depit oh kin mweidohng en kin weuwa sapwellime dipwisoun mahwen kan.
\v 22 Sohl ahpw ketin kadaralahng Sehsi pakair wet: “I kesempwaliki Depit. Komw mweidohng pwe en kin mihmi rehi oh doadoahkohng ie.”
\v 23 Eri, sang rahno kohla, ahnsou koaros me ngehn suwed me Koht ketin kadarodo kin ti pohn Sohl, Depit kin ale nah arp oh kesengki. Ngehn suwedo ahpw kin kohieisang, oh Sohl ahpw kin nsenamwahula oh pwurehng kehlailda.
\c 17
\s1 Kolaiad men Peiong mehn Israel ko
\p 
\v 1 Mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw pokonpene nan Soko, kahnimw en Suda ehu, pwe re en mahwen. Re ahpw kauwada imwarail impwal kan wasa kis me adaneki Epes Dammim, nanpwungen Soko oh Aseka.
\v 2 Sohl oh mehn Israel ko ahpw pokonpene oh pil kauwada imwarail impwal ko nan Wahun Elah, wasa re onopadahn mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan.
\v 3 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri irekla pohn ehu dohl, a mehn Israel ko pohn ehu, oh wahu ehu mi nanpwungarail.
\p 
\v 4 Ohl emen ede Kolaiad, sang nan kahnimw Kad, ahpw kohieido sang nan kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia ko oh men peiong mehn Israel ko. E reireiki piht duwau,
\v 5 oh e lisoaropki lisoarop mete prons ehu oh likawih likou mete prons me toutouki pohnangin paun 125.
\v 6 Denge ko pil kidikidki prons; oh e pil wa ketieun likimwei me wiawihkihda prons pohn pwopwe.
\v 7 Ahlap en nah ketieu wehte ahlap en tuhkehn pilaik laud pwoat, oh toutoun imwin ketieuwo kerengiong paun 15. Sounpei men kin tieng mwowe, wa nah mehn sansaro.
\v 8 Kolaiad eri uhda oh werlahng mehn Israel ko, nda, “Dahme kumwail wiewia men? Kumwail men mahwen? Iet ngehi mehn Pilisdia men, a kumwail lidun Sohl! Kumwail pilada emen kumwail pwe en peiong ie.
\v 9 Ma e pahn kana oh kemeiehla, se pahn wiahla amwail lidu; a ma I kana oh kemehla, kumwail pahn wiahla at lidu.
\v 10 Iet ngehi me men peiong karis en mehn Israel kan. Kumwail pilodohng ie emen ohl kommwaden, pwe se en pei!”
\v 11 Eri, ni Sohl oh sapwellime sounpei ko rongada met, re inenen masepwehkada.
\s1 Depit nan Kahnimpwal en Sohl
\p 
\v 12 Depit nein Sehsi, oh Sehsi mehn Eprat sang Pedleem nan Suda. Nein Sehsi pwutak me welimen, ni ahnsou me Sohl wia nanmwarki, ni ahnsowo Sehsi inenen likeilapalahr.
\v 13 Nah pwutak silimen me keieu laud ko iang Sohl ketila mahwen. Eden me keieu laudo, iei Eliap, me keriemeno, Apinadap, oh me kesilimeno, Samma.
\v 14 Me keieu tikitiko adaneki Depit. Eri, me laud silimen ko kin mihmi rehn Sohl,
\v 15 a Depit kin pwurala Pedleem ekei ahnsou, pwe en kin apwalih nein eh pahpao nah pelin sihpw.
\p 
\v 16 Kolaiad ahpw kin uhda oh men peiong mehn Israel ko nimenseng koaros oh nin soutik koaros erein rahn 40.
\p 
\v 17 Eri, rahn ehu, Sehsi ahpw ndaiong Depit, “Kilang, ale edin werentuhke inihnda pwukat, oh lopwon en pilawa 10 pwukat, oh tangahkihwei rehn riomw kan nan kahnimpwalo.
\v 18 Pil wawohng kaunen sounpeio seke sihs 10 pwukat. Ke ahpw kilang ia iren riomw kan, oh wahdo mehkot me pahn kadehdehda me ke tuhwong irail oh ma re me nsenamwahu.
\v 19 Nanmwarki Sohl, oh riomw kan, oh mehn Israel ko koaros, re ketiket nan Wahun Elah, mahmahweniong mehn Pilisida kan.”
\p 
\v 20 Eri, mandahn rahno, nimensehngie, Depit ahpw pwourda, oh mwurin eh kehkehlingkihong emen en apwahpwalih pelin sihpw ko, e ahpw ale kisin tungoal ako oh kohkohla duwen me Sehsi ndahng. E ahpw lel ni kahnimpwalo ni ahnsou me mehn Israel ko mwekimwekidieilahng wasahn mahweno, oh wie kadekadekedek kohla.
\v 21 Eri, karis en mehn Pilisdia ko oh mehn Israel ko ahpw irekla nan dewerail, sohpeipene.
\v 22 Depit eri pwilikihdi kisin tungoal akan rehn sounapwalih kisin mwenge kan, e ahpw tangala ni lainen mahweno rehn rie ko, oh idek rehrail ia irarail.
\v 23 Nindokon eh koasoakoasoiong irail, Kolaiad ahpw aludahdo sang rehn mehn Pilisdia kan oh kakahsdohng mehn Israel ko; nin duwen eh kin wia mahso. Depit eri rongada eh lokolokaia lemei.
\v 24 Ni ahnsou me mehn Israel ko kilangada Kolaiad, re masapwehkadahte tangdoaui.
\v 25 Re ahpw kin ndindapene, “Kilang, io ih! Kumwail rong dahme e kakahski. Mehmen me pahn kemehla, dene nanmwarki pahn ketikihong kepwe tohto, iangahki sapwellime serepein pwe en pwoudiki; oh e pahn ketin mahkikihong peneineien eh pahpa soangen daksis koaros.”
\p 
\v 26 Depit ahpw idek rehn me mihmi mpe ko, “Dahme pahn pweisen ohl me pahn kemehla mehn Pilisdia menet oh kapitasang Israel nan kanamenek wet? Pwe ihs ohl rotorot menen me kak pelianda karis en Koht ieias?”
\v 27 Irail eri ndaiong dahme pahn wiawihong ohl me pahn kemehla Kolaiad.
\p 
\v 28 Eliap, rien Depit me keieu laudo, ahpw rongada duwen Depit eh koasoakoasoiong aramas ako. E ahpw lingeringerkihda oh ndahng Depit, “Dahme ke wiewia met? Ihs me apwahpwalih noumw pelin sihpw ko nan sapwtehno? Mwalaun oh aklapalap aramas emen kowehn! I ese me ke kohdohn kilangete mahwenet!”
\p 
\v 29 Depit ahpw sapeng, kehtihtihki, “Pwe dah? Dahme I wiahda? Dene I sohte kak idek mehkot?”
\v 30 Ih eri sohpeilahng ohl emen oh wiahiong soangen peidekohte. Eri, ahnsou koaros me e pahn wia peidek wet, soangen pasapengohte me e kin ale.
\p 
\v 31 Ohl ekei me rongada en Depit eh koasoi ko ahpw ndahng Sohl. Sohl eri likwerihodo Depit.
\v 32 Depit eri patohwanohng Sohl, “Maing, Wasa Lapalap, kitail dehr masak mehn Pilisdia menet! Ngehi me pahn kohla oh peiong.”
\p 
\v 33 A Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “Soh! Sohte kak! Ia duwen omw pahn peiong, nan omw kisin pwutak emen? A ih, e sounpei sang ni eh pwulopwul.”
\p 
\v 34 Depit eri sapeng Sohl, patohwan, “I kin apwahpwalih nein pahpa pelin sihpw. Ahnsou koaros me laion men de pehr men pahn kin wahsang emen sihmpwul,
\v 35 I kin pwakih oh peiong; oh adihasang sihmpwulo. A ma laiono de pehro kin sohpeiong ie, I kin daperete, padikpene tepinwere, suk oh kemehla.
\v 36 I kemelahr laion oh pehr kei, oh I pil pahn wiahiong mehn Pilisdia rotorot menet me peliandahr karis en Koht ieias.
\v 37 KAUN-O ketin doareiesang laion kan oh pehr kan; e pil pahn ketin doareiesang mehn Pilisdia menet.”
\p Sohl eri sapeng Depit, mahsanih, “Eri, me mwahu! Kohwei, oh KAUN-O en ketin ieiang uhk.”
\v 38 E ahpw ketikihong Depit sapwellime likoun mahwen ko pwe en pwuhriong loale. E pil ketikidahng pohn moangen Depit lisoarop prons ehu, oh kapwuhrohng Depit nan likou mete.
\v 39 Depit ahpw kamwotowihedi nein Sohl kedlahso pohn likou meteo, oh song en alu; ahpw sohte kak, pwehki e sahn wa soangen dipwisou pwukat. E ahpw patohwanohng Sohl, “I sohte kak peiki soangen dipwisou pwukat. I sahn kowahlap.” Ih eri pwuhrsang loale oh kihsang koaruhsie.
\v 40 E ahpw ale nah sokon en silepen sihpwo, oh rikada kisin painwed medendel limau sang nan piletik pwoat oh kihdiong nan eh ehd. Eri, e ahpw kohieila, wa nah pahio, pwe en tuhwong Kolaiad.
\s1 Depit Kalowehdi Kolaiad
\p 
\v 41 Mehn Pilisdiao ahpw tapihada aludohng Depit, nah sounwa mehn sansaro me tieng. Eri, ni eh kerekerendohng Depit,
\v 42 oh kadehdehda mwomwe, e kouruhrki, pwehki eh mwomwen kisin pwutak masamwahu kis.
\v 43 Ih eri ndalahng Depit, “Mehnda sokon pwoaten? Ke lemeleme me ngehi kidi men?” E ahpw tapihada kahukihla ni mwaren eh koht kan oh peki re en keriahla Depit.
\v 44 E ahpw nda, “Nna, keido pwe I en wiahkihla kenen menpihr kan oh kenen mahn akan uduken paliweromwen.”
\p 
\v 45 Depit ahpw sapeng, nda, “Ke kohkodohng peikihong ie kedlahs, oh ketieu laud oh pil ketieu tikitik, a ngehi I pahn peikihong uhk mwaren KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap, Koht en karis en Israel kan, me ke peliandahr.
\v 46 Rahnwette KAUN-O pahn ketikihong uhk pahn ei manaman. I pahn poweiukedei, oh lupukasang moangomwen. Oh I pahn wiahkihla paliweren sounpei en Pilisdia kan kenen menpihr oh mahn akan kanarail kisin mwenge. Wehiet pwon pahn esehla me mie en Israel eh Koht.
\v 47 Eri, aramas koaros wasaht pahn kilang me e sohte ketin anahne kedlahs de ketieu pwe en kapitala sapwellime aramas akan. E kin ketin powehdi nan mahwen, oh e pahn ketikihong kumwail koaros pahn at manaman.”
\p 
\v 48 Kolaiad pil pwurehng tapihada keikeidohng Depit, a Depit mwadangete tenge lainen mahwen en mehn Pilisdia ko pwe en peiong.
\v 49 E ahpw ale takai ieu sang nan eh ehdo, oh kihong nan pahio oh kadaralahng Kolaiad. E lelete temwen Kolaiado kauwehla tihn moange. Kolaiad eri pwupwudiong nanpwel.
\v 50 Iei duwen Depit, ni eh sohte nah kedlahs, e ahpw kalowehdi oh kemehkihla Kolaiad pahi ehu oh takai ieu.\x - \xo 17:50 \xt 2 Sam. 21.19.\x*
\v 51 E ahpw mwadangete tenge Kolaiad, uhda powe, oh usadahsang nein Kolaiad kedlahso nan kidipe, oh lupukasang moangeo.
\p Ni mehn Pilisdia ko ar kilangada duwen nair ohl keieu kehlailo eh melahr, re ahpw tangdoaui.\x - \xo 17:51 \xt 2 Sam. 21.29.\x*
\v 52 Mehn Israel ko oh mehn Suda ahpw pwakih irail weriwer lao irail koaros lel Kad oh ni ewen kelen Ekron. Mehn Pilisdia tohto me lellel nanial en kolahng Saaraim pil lellahng Kad oh Ekron.
\v 53 Mehn Israel ko eri pwurodo sang ar pwakihirailla oh kauwehla kahnimpwal en mehn Pilisdia ko.
\v 54 Depit eri ale moangen Kolaiado oh wahla Serusalem, ahpw e nekinekidte en Kolaiad eh dipwisoun mahwen ko nan imwe impwalo.
\s1 Depit Mwohn Sohl
\p 
\v 55 Eri, ni Sohl eh mahsanihada Depit eh kohkolahng peiong Kolaiad, e ahpw keinemwe rehn Apner, kaun lapalap en sapwellime karis kan, mahsanih, “Ihs pwutako?”
\p Apner ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “I ahpw sohte patohwan, maing.”
\p 
\v 56 Sohl ahpw mahsanih, “Kohwei oh esehdo, ihs mwo.”
\p 
\v 57 Eri, ni Depit eh pwuralahng nan kahnimpwalo mwurin eh kemehla Kolaiad, Apner ahpw kahrelahng rehn Sohl. Depit weuwahte ahnsowo moangen Kolaiad.
\v 58 Sohl eri keinemwe reh, mahsanih, “Nahn, nein ihs kowe?”
\p A Depit ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Ngehi nein Sehsi, sapwellimomwi ladu, mehn Pedleem.”
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 Eri, Sohl oh Depit ahpw kaerala ara koasoi; oh mwuhr, nein Sohl pwutak, Sonadan, inenen poakepoakehla Depit duwehte eh poakohng pein eh mour.
\v 2 Sohl eri ketin kolokolete Depit sang rahno kohla, oh sohte mweidohng en pwurala ni imweo.
\v 3 Sonadan oh Depit ahpw wiahda inou ehu, inoun perien nanpwungara, pwehki Sonadan eh poakepoake Depit kowahlap.
\v 4 Sonadan ahpw kihsang eh likou puhp oh kihong Depit, iangahki eh dipwisoun mahwen, nah kedlahs, nah ketieu oh eh kateng.
\v 5 Depit eri kin inenen pweida mwahu ni mehkoaros me Sohl kin mahsanih en wiahda. Iei me Sohl ketin kasapwiladahng nan dewen kaunen sapwellime karis. Met kaparanda sapwellimen Sohl sounpei ko oh sapwellime kaunen sounpei koaros.
\s1 Sohl Peiriniong Depit
\p 
\v 6 Eri, nindokon sounpei en Israel ko ar pwurupwurala, mwurin Depit eh kemehlahr Kolaiad, lihen kahnimw koaros en Israel ahpw kohieilahng kasamwo Sohl. Re ahpw kin kokoulki koul kaperen kei, kahkahlek, oh kesekesengki nair keseng en dampwurin oh lair kan.
\v 7 Nan ar kahlek kaperen kan re ahpw kin koulki koul pwoatet, me ketihtihki, “Sohl kemelahr aramas kid, a Depit aramas nen.” \x - \xo 18:7 \xt 1 Sam. 21.11; 29.5.\x*
\v 8 Sohl inenen nsensuwedkihla soangen koul pwoatet, e ahpw engiengda, mahsanih, “Re ndinda me Depit kemehla aramas 10,000, a ngehi mehte 1,000. A ihte me e saikinte wia, en wiahla nanmwarki.”
\v 9 Eri, sang ni rahno kohla, kupwur en peiriniong Depit me inenen laud.
\p 
\v 10 Eri, manda sang rahno, Koht ahpw ketin mweidohng ngehn suwed men en tiada pohn Sohl. Sohl ahpw kin engiengda mahmahsenmwahlseli nan tehnpeseo, duwehte aramas iahk emen. Depit ahpw wie kesekesengki nah arpo duwen eh kin epwehnki wia rahn koaros, a Sohl ketiketki nin lime ketieu pwoat.
\v 11 E ahpw mengimengloalki, “I pahn ilewediong nin dihden.” Eri, e ahpw doakoahki ketieu pak riapak; a Depit sarekala pak riapak.
\p 
\v 12 Eri, Sohl ahpw masakada mehlel Depit, pwehki KAUN-O eh ketin ieiang Depit, a e ketin likidmeliehla ih.
\v 13 Sohl eri kadarala Depit oh kasapwiladahng kaunen sounpei 1,000. Depit eri kaunda nah sounpei ko nan mahwen,
\v 14 oh kin pweida mwahu ni mehkoaros me e kin wia, pwehki KAUN-O eh kin ketin ieiang ih.
\v 15 Sohl ahpw mwahngihada en Depit eh pweida mwahu, oh eh masak Depit ahpw lalaudla.
\v 16 Eri, aramas koaros nan Israel oh Suda poakepoake Depit, pwehki eh kin pweida mwahu ni doadoahk en kakaun.
\s1 Depit Pwoudikihda sapwellimen Sohl Serepein
\p 
\v 17 Sohl eri mahsanihong Depit, “Iet nei serepein laud Merap. I pahn kihong uhk pwe ke en pwoudikihda, ma ke pahn papah ie nin duwen sounpei kommwad oh loalopwoat emen, oh ma ke pahn pil mahwenki sapwellimen KAUN-O pali.” (Pwe Sohl kupwukupwure me mehn Pilisdia kan pahn kemehla Depit, a pein ih en saledekla sang wiewia wet.)
\p 
\v 18 Depit ahpw sapeng patohwan, “Ihs ngehi oh ei peneinei pwe I en pwoudiki sapwellimen nanmwarki serepein?”
\v 19 Ahpw ni ahnsou me Merap pahn pwoudikihda Depit, Sohl ahpw ketikihong ohl emen, ede Adriel, mehn Mehola.
\p 
\v 20 Ahpw sapwellimen Sohl serepein Maikal mwahukihda kowahlap Depit, oh ni Sohl eh mwahngihada met, e inenen kupwurperenkihda.
\v 21 E ahpw mengimengloalki, “I pahn kihong Depit nei serepein Maikal. E ahpw pahn widingehdi, oh mehn Pilisdia kan pahn kemehla.” Eri, Sohl ahpw mahsanihong Depit keriapak, “Ke pahn pwoudiki nei serepein.”
\v 22 E ahpw mahsanihong sapwellime lapalap ako re en ndaiong Depit ni rir, “Nanmwarki inenen kupwurperenkin uhk, oh sapwellime lapalap akan kin poakepoakeiuk. Iei me ahnsou wet iei ahnsou me ke pahn kapwopwoudiong sapwellime serepeino.”
\v 23 Eri, irail ndaiong Depit duwen met, a e sapengkin irail, patohwan, “Mehlel pwe ma emen pahn pwoudiki sapwellimen nanmwarki serepein, a e pahn wahunla. A ia duwen soangen aramas semwehmwe oh tikitik men ngehiet, e warohng?”
\p 
\v 24 Lapalap ako eri patohwanohng Sohl duwen me Depit patohwanehr.
\v 25 A Sohl mahsanihong irail re en patohwanohng Depit: “Ihte me nanmwarki kupwurki ke en pwainki sapwellime serepeino, iei kilin nein mehn Pilisdia me sarawi 100 me mehla, mehn ikihong sapwellime imwintihti kan.” (Met iei duwen Sohl eh koasoanehdi nan kupwure pwe Depit en kamakamala rehn mehn Pilisdia kan.)
\v 26 Eri, sapwellimen Sohl lapalap ako ahpw pakairkihong Depit mahsen en Sohl. Depit eri perenkihda eh pahn pwoudiki sapwellimen nanmwarki serepeino. Eri, mwohn rahnen kapwopwoudo,
\v 27 Depit oh nah sounpei ko kohla kemehla mehn Pilisdia 200. E ahpw wa kohdo kilin nair sarawi ko rehn nanmwarkio oh wadekada mwowe, pwe en kak pwoudiki sapwellime serepein. Sohl eri ketikihong Maikal pwe en pwoudiki.
\p 
\v 28 Sohl ahpw inenen mwahngihala mehlel duwen KAUN-O eh ketin ieiang Depit oh pil duwen sapwellime serepein Maikal eh inenen poakepoake.
\v 29 Iei me e masakada mehlel Depit sang mahs, oh wiahki eh imwintihti nindokon eh ieias.
\p 
\v 30 Eri, karis en mehn Pilisdia ko kin kohdo pwe re en mahwen, a ahnsou koaros Depit kin pweida mwahusang sapwellimen Sohl lapalap teikan. Ihme Depit ndandkihla kowahlap.
\c 19
\s1 Depit Diar Lokolok sang rehn Sohl
\p 
\v 1 Eri, Sohl ahpw mahsanihong sapwellime pwutak Sonadan oh sapwellime pwutak koaros me e kupwukupwure en kemehla Depit. Ahpw Sonadan inenen kin poakepoake Depit.
\v 2 Ih eri padahkihong Depit, “Ei pahpao songosong en kemeiukala. Eri, ke pahn kanahieng nimenseng en lakapw. Rukula wasa me rir oh mihmihte wasao.
\v 3 A I pahn kohla oh mihmi rehn ei pahpao nan mohso, wasa ke rukuruk ie, oh I pahn patohwanohng duwen kowe. Ma mie mehkot me pwarada, I pahn kairehkin uhk.”
\p 
\v 4 Sonadan eri patohwanda kapingpen Depit mwohn Sohl, oh ketihtihki, “Maing, komw dehr ketin wiahda mehkot me pahn kauwehla sapwellimomwi ladu Depit. Pwe ih, e sohte mwahn wiahda mehkot suwed ong komwi. Pwe mehkoaros me e kin wia, mihmi ni kamwahu laud ong komwi.
\v 5 E kereniong mehla ni eh kemehla Kolaiad, a KAUN-O ketikihong Israel en powehdi Kolaiad. Komw pein mahsanih oh kupwurperenkihda. Eri, ia kahrepen omwi pahn kauwehla ohl emen me sohte dipe, oh kemehla Depit ni sohte kahrepe?”
\p 
\v 6 Sohl ahpw ketin karonge dahme Sonadan patopatohwanohng. Eri, e ahpw kahukihla ni mwaren KAUN-O me Depit sohte pahn kamakamala.
\v 7 Sonadan eri ekerodo Depit oh padahkihong mehkoaros. Ih eri kahrehla Depit rehn Sohl, oh Depit ahpw pwurehng papah nanmwarkio duwehte mahs.
\p 
\v 8 Eri, mahwen ehu ahpw pwurehng wiawi nanpwungen mehn Israel oh mehn Pilisdia kan. Depit ahpw iang mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan oh kaloweiraildi, irail koaros eri tangdoaui.
\p 
\v 9 Rahn ehu, KAUN-O ahpw ketin mweidohng ngehn suwed en tiada pohn Sohl. Sohl ketiket nan mwoale ketiki nin lime ketieu pwoat, a Depit pil iang pato wasao, wie kesekesengki nah arp.
\v 10 Sohl eri song en doakoahki Depit sapwellime ketieuo pwe en ilewediong nin dihdo. A Depit ahpw sarek, ketieuo pa uhsang nin dihdo. Depit eri tangdoaui.
\p 
\v 11 Nipwongohte, Sohl ahpw ketin kadarala aramas ekei pwe re en mwasamwasahn imwen Depito oh kemehla nimensengo. Maikal, en Depit eh pwoud, ahpw padahkihong Depit, “Ma ke sohte pahn tangdoaui nipwongette, lakapw ke pahn kamakamala.”\x - \xo 19:11 \xt Mel. 59 Title.\x*
\v 12 Eh pwoudo eri kadaridi Depit sang pohn wenihmwtok ehu, e ahpw tangdoaui.
\v 13 Liho eri ale neira dikedik en eni oh kawendiong pohn pehto, oh uluhl ehu me wiawihkihda wunen kuht, e ahpw kihdiong pahn moangen dikediko; ih eri pwainkihdi pweinen pehto.
\v 14 Ni sapwellimen Sohl aramas ako ar lel wasao pwe re en ale Depit, Maikal padahkihong irail me Depit wonohnki eh soumwahu.
\v 15 Sohl ahpw pwurehng kadarirail pwe re en pein tuhwong Depit. E ahpw mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail wahdo ni eh mihmi nan eh pehto oh I ahpw pahn kemehla.”
\v 16 Irail eri patohla oh pedolong nan ihmwo, oh diarada dikediko nan pehto, oh uluhl wunen kuhto pahn moange.
\v 17 Sohl eri keinemwe rehn Maikal, “Dahme ke pitihkin ie nin duwe met oh kapitala ei imwintihtio?”
\p A e sapeng, patohwan, “Ahki e ndaiong ie me e pahn kemeiehla ma I sohte pahn sewese kapitala.”
\p 
\v 18 Depit eri pitla oh kohla rehn Samuel nan Rama oh padahkihong mehkoaros me Sohl ketin wiahiong. Ih oh Samuel ahpw kohla Naiod oh mihmi wasao.
\v 19 Rongen Depit eh mihmi Naiod, nan Rama, ahpw lel Sohl.
\v 20 Sohl eri ketin kadarala aramas ekei pwe re en salihedi Depit. Irail ahpw kilangada pwihnen soukohp ehu me wie kahkahlek oh weriwer, oh Samuel me arail sounkaweid. Ngenen Koht eri ti pohn sapwellimen Sohl aramas ako; irail ahpw pil iangada kahkahlek oh weriwer.
\v 21 Ni Sohl eh karongehda irair wet, e ahpw pil kadarala ekei meninkeder, a meninkeder ko pil iangada kahkahlek oh weriwer. E ahpw pil ketin kadarala meninkeder kei kasilipak, a sohngohte pil wiahiong irail.
\v 22 Eri, pein ih ahpw ketin piserla Rama. Ni eh ketin lel ni pwarer laud en Seku, e ahpw keinemwe wasa me Samuel oh Depit mihmi ie, a re sapengki me ira patopato Naiod.
\v 23 Eri, ni eh ketiket kolahng wasao, ngenen Koht ahpw pil ti powe, ih eri pil tapihada kahkahlek oh weriwer kohla lao lel Naiod.
\v 24 E ahpw ketikihsang sapwellime likou kan oh kahlekda oh weriwer mwohn Samuel. Eri, erein rahno pwon oh pil pwohngo pwon eh wonohn kilisou. (Iei wasa me mahseno tepisang ie, me ketihtihki, “Sohl pil wiahla soukohp emen?”)\x - \xo 19:24 \xt 1 Sam. 10.11-12.\x*
\c 20
\s1 Sonadan Sewese Depit
\p 
\v 1 Depit eri tangasang Naiod, nan Rama, tangalahng rehn Sonadan oh ndaiong, “Dahme I wiadahr? Dihp da me I dipkidahr? Sapwung da me I wiahiong omw pahpao me kahrehiong eh men kemeiehla?”
\p 
\v 2 Sonadan ahpw sapeng, nda, “Ke dehr perki mehkot, ke sohte pahn mehla! Ei pahpao kin mahsanihong ie mehkoaros me e kin ketin wiahda, me kesempwal oh sohte kesempwal, oh e sohte pahn ekihsang ie mewet. Soh! E sohte kak!”
\p 
\v 3 A Depit sapeng, ketihtihki, “Omw pahpao inenen mwahngih mwahu duwen omw poakepoake ie, oh e koasoanehdi nan kupwure me e sohte pahn kasalehiong uhk dahme e kupwukupwurehiong ie, pwe e de kauweiukala. I kakete kahukihla ni mwaren KAUN-O me I sohte dohsang ei pahn mehla.”
\p 
\v 4 Sonadan ahpw sapeng, nda, “Eri, I pahn wia mehkoaros me ke anahne.”
\p 
\v 5 Depit eri sapeng, nda, “Kilang, lakapw iei rahn Sarawien Maram Pwul, rahn me I kin epwehnki iang nanmwarki ketidiong nin tehpel. Eri, ma ke mweidohng ie, I pahn kolahng rukula nansapw lel nin soutik en pali.\x - \xo 20:5 \xt Nemp 28.11.\x*
\v 6 Ma omw pahpao pahn tehkada me I sohte iang mihmi nin tehpelo, a menlau padahkihong me I pekihda rehmw mweimwei pwe I en patolahng mahs ni imweio nan Pedleem, pwe ih ahnsoun at peneinei ar kin wia at sarawien meirong nan sounpar koaros.
\v 7 Eri, ma e pahn mahsanih, “Me mwahu,” eri, I pahn nsenamwahu oh pitla. A ma e engiengda, ke pahn esehki me e ketin koasoanehdi en kemeiehla.
\v 8 Menlau kapwaiada ei pekipeket, oh kapwaiada inou sarawi me ke wiahiong ie. Ahpw ma I dipadahr, eri a, ke nek pein kemeiehla. Dahme omw pahpao me pahn kemehkiniehla?”
\p 
\v 9 Sonadan ahpw sapeng, nda, “Ke dehr lemeleme soahngen. Ma I uhdahn ese me ei pahpao koasoanehdi nan kupwure en kemeiukala, I uhdahn pahn kairehkin uhk.”
\p 
\v 10 Depit eri idek reh, “A ihs me pahn kairehkin ie, ma omw pahpao sapeng uhk nan eh engieng?”
\p 
\v 11 Sonadan ahpw sapeng Depit, nda, “Kita kohieila nan mohso.” Ira eri kohieila,
\v 12 oh Sonadan ndahng Depit, “KAUN-O, Koht en Israel, en ketin wia ata sounkadehde, lakapw, ni soangen ahnsou wet, oh pil pali, I pahn idek rehn ei pahpao. Ma e pahn mwomwen kadek ong uhk, I pahn pakairkihong uhk.
\v 13 A ma e kupwukupwure en kauweiukala, KAUN-O en ketin kemeiehla ma I sohte pahn pakairkihong uhk oh kadaralahng uhk wasa me ke kak rukula ie. KAUN-O en ketiket rehmw duwehte eh kin ketin ieiang ei pahpao!
\v 14 A ma I pahn momourte, menlau kapwaiada omw inouwen oh loalopwoatohng ie; ahpw ma I mehla,
\v 15 kadekohng ei peineinei ahnsou koaros. Eri, ahnsou me KAUN-O pahn ketin kamwomwala douluhl omwi imwintihti kan koaros,\x - \xo 20:15 \xt 2 Sam. 9.1.\x*
\v 16 ata inou wet pahn poatopoatte, sohte pahn ohla. Ma e pahn ohla, KAUN-O pahn ketin kalokeiuk.”
\p 
\v 17 Sonadan eri pwurehng koangngoangehki Depit en pwurehng wiahda inoun limpoak ong ih, pwe Sonadan poakepoake mehlel Depit duwehte eh kin poakohng pein eh mour.
\v 18 Sonadan eri ndaiong Depit, “Lakapw, iei rahn Sarawien Maram Pwul; oh ma ke sohte iang mi wasao, re pahn tehkada omw sohte iang kasarawio.
\v 19 Oh pil pali, ma ke sohte iang, re pahn inenen tehkada. Eri, kohwei wasaohte me ke rukula ie mahso, oh rukula palio kasukasuk en takaio.
\v 20 Eri, I ahpw pahn kadaralahng kanengen kesik ketieu silipwoat, mwomwen me I songosong kaskih mehkot.
\v 21 I ahpw pahn ndaiong ei ladu en kohla rapahkihdo. Eri, ma I ndaiong, ‘Kilang, pwe kanengen kesik ketieu ko mihmi palihdo sang uhk; ale oh wahdo;’ met wehwehki me ke pitlahr. Eri, ke pahn kohdo rehi. Ke dehpa perki mehkot.
\v 22 A ma I ndaiong, ‘Kanengen kesik ketieu ko mihmi palihla sang uhk;’ eri kohkohwei, pwe iei kupwur en KAUN-O men.
\v 23 A duwen inou me kita wiahda nanpwungata, KAUN-O pahn ketin kupwure pwe kita en kin dadaurete.”
\p 
\v 24 Depit eri rukula nansapwo. Ni ahnsoun Sarawien Maram Pwulo, Nanmwarki Sohl ahpw ketido
\v 25 oh ketidiong nan mwoale limwahn dihdo. Apner mwohd limwah, a Sonadan mwohd mwowe palio tehpelo. A sohte aramas nan dewen Depito.
\v 26 Ahpw Sohl sohte mahsanih mehkot rahno, pwe e kupwukupwure, “Ele mehkot wiawihong Depit oh e sohte mwakelekeliong sarawiet.”
\v 27 Mandahn rahno, mwurin Sarawien Maram Pwulo, dewen Depito pil tetehnte. Iei me Sohl keinemwe rehn Sonadan, “Dahme Depit sohte iangki kamadipw wet aio oh rahnwet?”
\p 
\v 28 A Sonadan sapeng, patohwan, “Ahki e pekihda rehi en patolahng Pedleem.
\v 29 E patohwanohng ie, ‘Menlau mweidohng ie, pwe at peneinei pahn wia kasarawihpen at meirong en pahr nan kanimwo, oh rieio koasoanehdi I en iang mi wasao. Eri, ma kowe uhdahn kompoakepahi, a mweidohng ie I en kohla oh tuhwong mahs kisehi ko.’ Eri, ih kahrepen eh sohte mi nan dewe ni sapwellimomwi tehpelet.”
\p 
\v 30 Sohl eri engiengda kowahlap pahn Sonadan oh mahsanihong, “Ia uwen kahngohdi oh soaloalopwoat en omw nohno! I esehte me ke kin uhpalihki Depit, iei me ke kauwehkilahr pein kowe oh pil eden omw nohno!
\v 31 Eri, ke ese pwe nindokon Depit eh momour, ke sohte mwahn kak wiahla nanmwarkien wehiet. Ahnsou wette kohwei oh wahdo rehi wasaht, pwe e uhdahn pahn kamakamala.”
\p 
\v 32 Sonadan eri sapeng, patohwan, “Dahme e pahn kamakamkihla? Sapwung da me e wiahda?”
\p 
\v 33 Ni ahnsowohte Sohl doakoahki sapwellime ketieuo Sonadan pwe en kemehla. Sonadan ahpw esehkihda me eh pahpao koasoanedier nan kupwure me e pahn ketin kemehla Depit.
\v 34 Sonadan eri uhda sang nin tehpelo, nan kapehde inenen lingeringer. Ihme e sohte mwahn mwengehki ni keriaun rahnen Sarawien Maram Pwulo. E inenen nsensuwedkihla Depit, pwehki eh pahpao e ketin kamwamwahlihala.
\v 35 Nimenseng en mandahn rahno, Sonadan ahpw kohla rehn Depit nan mohso, duwen ara inoukipene. E ahpw kahrehda kisin pwutak kis.
\v 36 Ih eri ndaiong kisin pwutako, “Ke pahn tangewei oh ale kanengen kesik ketieu kan me I pahn kadar.” Kisin pwutako eri tangala, a Sonadan kadar kanengen kesik ieu me pwupw palila sang.
\v 37 Ni kisin pwutako eh lel wasa me kanengen kesik ketieuo pwupwudi ieo, Sonadan ahpw wering, nda, “E pwupwudi keileweisang!
\v 38 Mwadahng! Ke dehr uhdi!” Kisin pwutako rikada kanengen kesik ketieuo oh pwurodohng rehn Sonadan.
\v 39 E ahpw sehse da wehwehn tiahko; a Sonadan oh Depit kelehpw me ese.
\v 40 Sonadan eri kihong kisin pwutako nah dipwisoun mahwen ko oh ndaiong en kapwurehla nan kahnimwo.
\p 
\v 41 Eri, mwurin kisin pwutako eh samwalahr, Depit ahpw kesihnenda palio kasukasuk en takaio. E ahpw poaridiong nanpwelo pak siluh. Ih oh Sonadan ahpw wie sengiseng oh emente metik mesen emen; en Depit eh nsensuwed inenen laudsang en Sonadan.
\v 42 Sonadan eri ndaiong Depit, “Koht en ketin ieiang uhk. KAUN-O pahn ketin kupwure pwe kowe oh ngehi, oh kadaudokomw kan oh pil kadaudokei kan, kitail en kin dadaurete inou sarawi me kita kauwadahr nanpwungata.” Depit eri mwesel kohkohla, a Sonadan pwurala nan kahnimwo.
\c 21
\s1 Depit Tangasang Sohl
\p 
\v 1 Depit eri kohkohla rehn samworo Ahimelek nan Nop. Ahimelek inenen pwuriamweikihla oh rerrer ni eh kilangada Depit, e ahpw idek, “Dahme ke kelehpwki kohdo met?”\x - \xo 21:1 \xt Mad. 12.3-4; Mk 2.15-26; Luk 6.3.\x*
\p 
\v 2 Depit eri sapeng, patohwan, “Poaron en nanmwarki ehu me I patohwando. Mwohnsapwo ketin kehkehlingkihong ie I en dehpa kasalehiong emen audepen poaron wet. Iei me I patohwanohng nei aramas ako re en awih ie oh tuhwong ie wasa kis.
\v 3 Eri, met kisin tungoal dah me mie rehmwi? Komw ketikihdo ei tungoal lopwon en pilawa limau de okotme tohtohr me mie rehmwi.”
\p 
\v 4 Samworo ahpw mahsanih, “Sohte pilawa mwahl mehn tungoal; ihte pilawa sarawi me mie. Ihme I kak kihwei ma noumw aramas akan sohte wiahda nsenen pwopwoud ni ahnsou keren.”
\p 
\v 5 Depit eri sapeng samworo, patohwan, “Re sohte wia; nei aramas akan kin dadaurete ar mwakelekel ong kaudok pil duwehte ni ahnsou me re kin waseli ilek mwahl akan. Eri, ahpw mehlel soangen ahnsou wet me se patohwando poaron kesempwal wet.”
\p 
\v 6 Samworo eri ketikihong Depit pilawa me mie reh, me wialahr meirong ong Koht, me kohsang pohn tehpel sarawio, oh ekei me kapw ahpw wiliandi.\x - \xo 21:6 \xt Lip 24.5-9.\x*
\p 
\v 7 (Ni rahno, sapwellimen Sohl silepen sihpw keieu kehlail, ede Doek, mehn Edom, mihmi wasao pwehn wia pwukoa sarawi ehu.)
\p 
\v 8 Depit eri mahsanihong Ahimelek, “Mie ketieu de kedlahs rehmw me ke kak kihong ie? Poaron en nanmwarkio kahrehiong ei karuaru oh sohte ei ahnsou en wahda nei kedlahs de ehu soangen tehtehn mahwen.”
\p 
\v 9 Ahimelek ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Nein Kolaiad mehn Pilisdiao kedlahs me mihmi rehi, me komw kemehla nan Wahun Elah; eri kedlahso mihmi palio ihpodo. Ma komw kupwurki, komw kak ale, ihte tehte me mi wasaht.”\x - \xo 21:9 \xt 1 Sam. 17.51.\x*
\p Depit eri mahsanih, “Nna, patohwando. Sohte ehu kedlahs me mwahusang!”
\p 
\v 10 Depit eri mwesel, tangasang Sohl, oh kohkohla rehn Akis, nanmwarkien Kad.
\v 11 Sapwellimen nanmwarkio lapalap ako ahpw idek rehn Akis, “Kaidehn Depit met, nanmwarkien eh wehio? Ih ohlo met me lih akan kin kokouliong nindokon ar kin kahkahlek, ndinda, ‘Sohl kemehla kid, ahpw Depit kemehla nen.’”\x - \xo 21:11 \xt 1 Sam. 18.7; 29.5.\x*
\p 
\v 12 Pato pwukat ahpw kamwakidada kupwur en Depit, kahrehda eh masakada Nanmwarki Akis.\x - \xo 21:12 \xt Mel. 56 Title.\x*
\v 13 Karehda ahnsou koaros me Depit kin ketiket rehrail, e kin mwomwehda mwomwen aramas iahk ni ar kin koledi. E kin rakirakihseli ewen kelen kahnimwo oh pilen ewe kin kerekeredi nan eh alis kan.\x - \xo 21:13 \xt Mel. 34 Title.\x*
\v 14 Akis eri mahsanihong sapwellime lapalap ako, “Kumwail kilang aramas iahk emen men. Dahme kumwail wahkidohng ie?
\v 15 E seu itarehr uwen tohtohn aramas iahk rehi? Mehnda kumwail pil wadohng mehmen en rehi pwehn kedirapwahkin ie eh mwekid en sahliel kan nan imweiet?”
\c 22
\s1 Kamkamalahn Samworo kan
\p 
\v 1 Depit tangasang nan kahnimw Kad oh tangala nan peden paip ehu limwahn kahnimw Adullam. Ni ahnsou me rie ko oh eh peneinei rongada irair wet, re kohla oh iangala ih.\x - \xo 22:1 \xt Mel. 57 Title; Mel. 142 Title.\x*
\v 2 Aramas akan me milahr pahn kehnaudek de pweipwahndlahr de nsensuwedlahr pil iangala ih, e ahpw wiahla arail kaun, irail koaros patpene me pahpwiki samwa.
\p 
\v 3 Depit eri ketsang wasao ketlahng Mispa nan Mohap. E ahpw patohwanohng nanmwarkien Mohap, “Komw ketin mweidohng ei pahpa oh nohno en patohdo rehmwi oh patopato met I lao patohwan diarada kupwur en Koht ong ie.”
\v 4 Depit eri ketikihdi eh nohno oh pahpa rehn nanmwarkien Mohap; ira eri mihmihte rehn nanmwarkio nindokon Depit eh rukuruk nan peden paipo.
\p 
\v 5 Soukohp Kad ahpw pwarodo rehn Depit oh patohwanohng, “Komw dehr ketiket met; mwadang ketla nan wehin Suda.” Depit eri mwadangete ketla sang wasao ketiketlahng nanwel en Ered.
\p 
\v 6 Rahn ehu Sohl ketiket Kipea, mwomwohd pahn tuhke damarisk pwoat nin dohl ehu, oh kolokol nah ketieu, oh sapwellime sounpei kan kesikesihnen kapikapil. Re padahkihong me Depit oh nah aramas akan dierekier,
\v 7 e ahpw mahsanihong sapwellime sounpei ko, “Kumwail rong, kumwail nein Pensamin. Kumwail lemeleme me Depit pahn kihong kumwail koaros sahpw oh mwetin wain oh wiahkinkumwailla lapalap en sapwellime karis?
\v 8 Ihme kumwail wiewiahki en uhwong ie? Sohte emen kumwail me padahkihong ie me nei pwutako wiadahr inou ehu ong Depit. Sohte emen kumwail me nsenohkin ie de padahkihong ie me Depit, emen nei aramas, raparapahki ahnsou mwahu met en kemeiehla, oh nei pwutako me koangngoangehki!”
\p 
\v 9 Doek kesikesihnen wasao limwahn sapwellimen Sohl sounpei ko, ahpw patohwan, “I kilangehr Depit ni eh patohla rehn Ahimelek, nein Ahidup, nan Nop.\x - \xo 22:9 \xt 1 Sam. 21.7-9; Mel. 52 Title.\x*
\v 10 Ahimelek ahpw kalelapak rehn KAUN-O dahme Depit pahn wia, ih eri patohwanohng Depit kisin sak oh nein Kolaiad mehn Pilisdiao nah kedlahso.”
\p 
\v 11 Nanmwarki Sohl eri poaronlahng samworo Ahimelek oh kiseh kan koaros, me pil wia samworo kei nan Nop, re en pwarodo reh.
\v 12 Sohl eri mahsanihong Ahimelek, “Rong, kowe Ahimelek.”
\p A Ahimelek sapeng, patohwan, “Iet ngehi sapwellimomwi ladu.”
\p 
\v 13 Sohl eri keinemwe reh, “Dahme kowe oh Depit koasoakoasoanehki kumwa en uhwong ie? Dahme ke kihongki kisin sak oh kedlahs, oh pekihki rehn Koht kaweid ni mware? Met e uhwongieier oh mwasamwasahn ahnsou mwahu en kemeiehla!”
\p 
\v 14 Ahimelek sapeng, patohwan, “Maing, Depit iei sapwellimomwi lapalap me keieu loalopwoat! E pil pwoudiki sapwellimomwi serepein, e pil wia kaunen sounpei kan me kin sinsilei komwi, oh aramas koaros nan tehnpesomwi kin wauneki.
\v 15 Ei, I patohwan peki rehn KAUN-O ni mware, oh kaidehn keieun ei wia met. Ahpw ong ni iren koasoakoasoane mwekid en uhwong Wasa Lapalap, komw dehr kapwukoakin ie de emen ei peneinei. I sohte ese duwen mwekid wet!”
\v 16 Nanmwarkio eri mahsanih, “Ahimelek, kowe oh kisehmw kan koaros pahn kamakamala.”
\v 17 E ahpw mahsanihlahng sounpei silepe ko me kesikesihnen limwah, “Kumwail kemehla samworo kan en Koht. Re iangehr Depit koasoanehdi mwekid en uhwong ie oh re sohte padahkihong ie me Depit tangehrdoaui nan ar ese mwekid pwukat koaros.” Ahpw silepe ko sohte men kemehla samworo ko en Koht, re nennenlahte sohte mwekid.
\v 18 Sohl eri mahsanihong Doek, “Komwi, Doek, komw kemeirailla.” Doek eri kemehla irail koaros. Rahno e kemehla samworo weliakan limmen me ahneki manaman en likawih ihpod.
\v 19 Sohl pil koasoanehdi pwe tohn Nop teikan koaros, kahnimw en samworo kan, en kamakamala: ohl oh lih, seri oh seri pwelel kan, kou, ahs, oh sihpw—koaruhsie kamakamala.
\p 
\v 20 Ahpw Apaiadar, emen nein Ahimelek pwutak ko, tangdoaui oh pitla, e ahpw kohla oh iangala Depit.
\v 21 E padahkihong Depit duwen Sohl e ketin kemehla samworo ko.
\v 22 Depit eri sapeng, mahsanih, “Ni ei kilangada Doek wasao rahno, I esehte me e pahn kairehki Sohl soahng koaros. Eri, ngehi me pwukoakidier kamakamalahn kisehmwail kan.
\v 23 Ke pahn mihmihte rehi oh ke dehr masak mehkot. Sohl men kemeikitahla koaros, ngehi oh kowe, ahpw sohte mehkot pahn lellohng uhk rehi.”
\c 23
\s1 Depit Kapitala Kahnimw Keila
\p 
\v 1 Depit rongada me mehn Pilisdia kan mahmahweniong kahnimw Keila oh piripirapasang wahn kohn kan me re ahpwtehn kihpene.
\v 2 Ih eri kalelapak rehn KAUN-O, patohwan, “Maing, I en patohla mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan?”
\p KAUN-O ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “Ei, mahweniong irail oh kapitala kahnimw Keila.”
\p 
\v 3 Sapwellimen Depit sounpei ko ahpw patohwanohng, “Komw mahsanih duwen at masepwehk wasaht nan Suda; e pahn ukla at masepwehk ma se pahn kohla mahweniong karis en Pilisdia kan!”
\v 4 Depit eri pwurehng kalelapak rehn KAUN-O, KAUN-O ahpw ketin mahsanihong, “Kohwei oh mahweniong Keila, pwehki I pahn ketikihong uhk pwe ke en powehdi mehn Pilisdia kan.”
\v 5 Depit oh sapwellime sounpei ko ahpw ketlahng Keila, oh mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan, re ahpw kemehla me ngeder rehrail oh wahsang neirail pelinmen kan. Ih duwen eh kapitala kahnimw Keila.
\p 
\v 6 Apaiadar nein Ahimelek wahsang ihpod ni ahnsou me e tangdoaui oh iangala Depit nan Keila.
\p 
\v 7 Re ahpw patohwanohng Sohl me Depit patolahngehr Keila; e ahpw mahsanih, “Koht ketikidier Depit pahn ei manaman. Depit pedolongehr nan lidip ehu me iei kahnimw me mie kehl kapilpene iangahki wenihmw kehlail kei.”
\v 8 Sohl eri kapokonepene sapwellime sounpei kan pwe re en mahwen, re en kolahng kahnimw Keila oh koledi Depit oh nah sounpei ko.
\p 
\v 9 Ahnsou me Depit rongada me Sohl koasoakoasoane en mahweniong, e patohwanohng samworo Apaiadar, “Komw patohwando ihpodo met.”
\v 10 Depit ahpw patohwanohng KAUN-O, “Maing KAUN, Koht en Israel, I rongehr me Sohl koasoakoasoane en patohdo Keila oh kamwomwala pwehki ngehi, sapwellimomwi ladu.
\v 11 Ia duwe, pwilidak en Keila kan pahn pangielahng rehn Sohl? Sohl uhdahn pahn patohdo, duwen me I rongehr? Maing KAUN, Koht en Israel, I patohwan peki komwi en ketin sapeng ie.”
\p KAUN-O ahpw ketin sapeng mahsanih, “Sohl pahn patohdo.”
\p 
\v 12 A Depit pwurehng patohwan, “A pwilidak en Keila kan pahn pangalahng Sohl ngehi oh nei sounpei kan?”
\p KAUN-O ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “Re pahn pangkumwailla.”
\p 
\v 13 Eri, Depit oh nah sounpei ko—koaros patpene kerenieng limepwiki—mwadangete kohkohla sang Keila. Ni Sohl eh rongada me Depit tangasangehr Keila, e ahpw kapweiekidi kupwure.
\s1 Depit nan Sahpw Nahnahn
\p 
\v 14 Depit wie rukurukselihte nan sahpw nahnahno, nan sapwtehn limwahn Sip. Sohl ahpw kin songosong raparapahki, ahpw Koht sohte ketin mweidohng en diar.
\v 15 Depit esehte me Sohl raparapahki pwehn kemehla.
\p Depit mihmihte Ores, nan sapwtehn limwahn Sip.
\v 16 Sonadan ahpw kohla reh oh koangngoangehki ndindaiong duwen eh Koht eh ketin sinsile.
\v 17 E patohwanohng Depit, ketihtihki, “Komw dehr masak mehkot. Ei pahpa Sohl sohte kak en kauweikomwihla. E ese mehlel me komwi me pahn wiahla nanmwarkien Israel oh ngehi me pahn keriaun kaun.”
\v 18 Ira riemeno ahpw wiahda inou sarawi ehu nanpwungara me ira pahn wiahla pirien ehu. Depit eri mihmihte Ores, a Sonadan pwurala ni imweo.\x - \xo 23:18 \xt 1 Sam. 18.3.\x*
\p 
\v 19 Aramas ekei sang Sip ahpw kohla rehn Sohl nan Kipea oh patohwanohng, “Depit wie rukurukseli nan sapwatail nan Ores nin Nahna Akila, ni palieir en sapwtehn en Suda.\x - \xo 23:19 \xt Mel. 54 Title.\x*
\v 20 Se patohwan ese, maing, Wasa Lapalap, uwen omwi kupwurki saikedi; eri komwi ketido nan sapwatet, se ahpw pahn sewesei komwi saikedi.”
\p 
\v 21 Sohl ahpw sapeng irail, mahsanih, “KAUN-O en ketin kupwuramwahwih kumwail pwehki amwail ngoang oh kadek ong ie.
\v 22 Kumwail pwurowei oh pwurehng tehk mwahu wasa e kin mihmi ie oh ihs me kilang ih wasao. I rong me e inenen kadek widing.
\v 23 Kumwail rapahkihda wasa kan me e kin rukuruk ie, oh kumwail mwadang pakairkihong ie. I ahpw pahn iang kumwail kohwei, oh ma e mihmihte wasao, I pahn salihedi, mehnda ma I pahn kohkohseli raparapahki nan Suda pwon.”
\p 
\v 24 Irail eri mwesel oh pwurala nan Sip mwohn Sohl. Depit oh nah sounpei ko mihmi nan sapwtehn en Maon, nan wahu tehn ehu ni palieir en sapwtehn en Suda.
\v 25 Sohl oh sapwellime sounpei ko eri mwesel pwe re en rapahki Depit, ahpw Depit rongada duwen mwekid wet, ih eri tangala nan wasa takain sapwtehn en Maon oh mihmi mwo. Ni Sohl eh rongada met, e ahpw pwakihala Depit.
\v 26 Sohl oh sapwellime sounpei ko ket ni apali dohlo, a Depit oh nah ko apali. Depit karukaruaru en tangasang Sohl oh sapwellime ko me songosong en kapilirailpene oh nektehn koliraildi.
\v 27 Ni ahnsowohte meninkeder kei pa leledo rehn Sohl oh patohwanohng, “Komw mwadang ketido, pwe mehn Pilisdia kan nektehn mahweniong nin limomwio.”
\v 28 Sohl eri tokedi sang pwakipwakih Depit, e ahpw ketila mahweniong mehn Pilisdia ko. Ih kahrepen wasao eh adanekihla Dohlen Tohrohrpeseng.
\v 29 Depit eri mwesel oh kohla nan sapwen Engkedi, wasa e patopato ie ni rir.
\c 24
\s1 Depit Kakehr Kemehla Sohl, ahpw Sohte Kemehla
\p 
\v 1 Eri, ni Sohl eh ketin sapahldo sang eh mahweniong mehn Pilisdia kan, pakair ahpw kohieng dene Depit mihmiseli nanwel en Engkedi.
\v 2 Sohl eri ketikihda sounpei keieu kommwad 3,000 sang rehn sapwellime sounpeien Israel ko, oh ketin rapahki Depit oh nah sounpei ko ni palimesehn Paipen Kuhten Wel kan.
\v 3 E ahpw lel pwoaren paip ehu me mi limwahn kelen pelin sihpw kei limwahnialo, e ahpw ketila pwe en lokowel. Depit oh nah sounpei ko wie rukuruk nan pwoaren paipo.\x - \xo 24:3 \xt Mel. 57 Title; Mel. 142 Title.\x*
\v 4 Re ahpw ndaiong Depit, “Ih omwi ahnsou met! KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong komwi me e pahn ketikihong pahn omwi manaman omwi imwintihtio, oh komw pahn kak wiahiong dahme komw mwahuki.” Depit eri kereplahte lupukasang kisin pwungipen sapwellimen Sohl likou reireio ni eh sohte ketin kehnda.
\v 5 Nan kapehd en Depit ahpw soansuwedkihda,
\v 6 e ahpw ndalahng nah sounpei ko, “KAUN-O en ketin irehdi sang ie pwe I en dehr wiahiong mehkot suwed ong ei kaun, me KAUN-O ketin pilada pwe en nanmwarki. I sohte pahn wiahiong mehkot suwed, pwe ih nanmwarki me KAUN-O ketin pilada.”\x - \xo 24:6 \xt 1 Sam. 26.11.\x*
\v 7 Depit eri irehkihdi koasoi pwukat nah sounpei ko pwe re dehr mahweniong Sohl.
\p Sohl eri ketieisang nan pwoaren paipo oh ketiketla.
\v 8 A Depit patohieila mwuri oh likwerih, patohwan, “Maing, Wasa Lapalap!” Sohl ahpw ketin pirekekla, a Depit poaridiong nanpwel,
\v 9 oh patohwan, “Maing, dahme komw kin ketin karongehki aramas akan me kin patopatohwan me I kin songosong en kauweikomwihla?
\v 10 Komw kak pein mahsanih duwen rahnwet KAUN-O eh ketikihong komwi pahn ei manaman nan pwoaren paipet. Ekei patohwanohng ie I en kemeikomwihla, I ahpw sohte kapwaiada, pwehki ei patohwan poakohng komwi oh ese me komwi me KAUN-O ketin pilada en nanmwarki.
\v 11 Semei, komw kadehde pwungipen omwi likou reirei me I kolokol nan pehiet. I lupukasang ni omwi likowen; ahpw I sohte kemeikomwihla. Met pahn kadehdehiong komwi duwen ei sohte men uhwong komwi de kauweikomwihla. Komw ketin raparapahkin ie pwe komwi en kemeiehla, ni ei sohte mwahn wiahiong komwi sapwung ehu.
\v 12 KAUN-O en ketin kadeikada ihs rehta me sapwung! En ketin kalokehkin komwi pwehki soahng kan me komw wiewiahiong ie, pwe ngehi I sohte pahn wia mehkot suwed ong komwi.
\v 13 Komw mwahngih lepin mahseno, ‘Aramas suwed kan me kin wiahda me suwed.’ Eri, I sohte pahn wiahiong komwi mehkot suwed.
\v 14 Komw mahsanih dahme nanmwarkien Israel songosong en kemehla! Ihs me e ketin pwakipwakih! E ketin pwakipwakih kidi mehla men! Likarak emen!\x - \xo 24:14 \xt 1 Sam. 26.20.\x*
\v 15 KAUN-O me pahn ketin kadeik kita oh pahn koasoanehdi ihs rehta me sapwung. En ketin kasawih irair wet, en ketin doareiehla oh kapitiehla sang komwi.”
\p 
\v 16 Ni ahnsou me Depit kanekehla eh koasoi, Sohl ahpw mahsanih, “Iei kowe men, Depit, nei pwutak?” Ih eri tapihada tentenihr.
\v 17 E ahpw mahsanihong Depit, “Kowe me pwung, a ngehi me sapwung! Ke inenen wiewia mwahu ong ie, a I ahpw wiahiong uhk soangen sapwung wet!
\v 18 Rahnwet ke kasalehda uwen omw mwahu ong ie, pwehki omw sohte kemeiehla ni KAUN-O eh ketikihong ie pahn omw manaman.
\v 19 Pwe ihs me kin koledi eh imwintihti oh mwuhr e ahpw kin kadarala, sohte wiahiong mehkot? Koht en ketin kupwuramwahwihkin uhk dahme ke wiahiong ie rahnwet.
\v 20 I ahpw dehdehkihla mehlel met me ke pahn wiahla nanmwarkien Israel, oh wehiet pahn mihmihte pahn omw manaman.
\v 21 Ahpw inoukihong ie ni mwaren KAUN-O me ke pahn kolokolete, sohte kasohrehla kadaudokei kan, pwe edeiet oh eden ei peneinei en dehr sohrala kohkohlahte.”
\v 22 Depit eri kahukihla me e pahn kapwaiada inou wet.
\p Sohl eri ketin sapahllahng ni tehnpeseo, a Depit oh ienge ko ahpw pwuralahng wasa re kin rukuruk ie.
\c 25
\s1 Sipallahn Samuel
\p 
\v 1 Samuel eri sipalla, oh mehn Israel koaros pokonpene oh mwahieiki. Irail eri sarepidi nan sousou ni imwe nan Rama.
\s1 Depit oh Apikail
\p Mwurin met, Depit ahpw kohkohla nan sapwtehn en Paran.
\v 2-3 Mie ohl emen me kisehn peneineien Kalep, ede Napal, mehn kahnimw Maon, me sapweniki sahpw ehu limwahn kahnimw Karmel. Ohl kepwehpwe men ih, me naineki sihpw silikid oh kuht kid. Eden eh pwoud Apikail, inenen masamwahu oh koahiek, ahpw ohlo me mihn oh lemei.
\p Napal wie sesehk nah kuht ko nan Karmel,
\v 4 oh Depit koukousoan nan sapwtehn en Paran, ahpw rongada met.
\v 5 Ih eri kadaralahng Napal mwahnakapw ehk oh kehkehlingkihong irail re en kohla Karmel, oh rapahkihda Napal, oh kihong eh rahnmwahu.
\v 6 E kehkehlingkihong irail re en ndaiong Napal, “Maing Napal, Depit patohwandohng komwi eh rahnmwahu oh kapaiamwahu ong omwi peneinei oh mehkoaros me sapwellimomwi.
\v 7 E patohwan rongada me komw wie sesehk noumwi sihpw kan, oh e men komwi en mwahngih me sapwellimomwi silepen sihpw kan ieiang kiht oh se sohte wiahiong irail mehkot suwed. Sohte arail mehkot pirapasang nindokon ar mihmi nan Karmel.
\v 8 Komw pahn ketin kalelapak rehrail, re ahpw pahn patohwanohng komwi. Se leledo wasaht rahn sarawi ehu, oh Depit patohwan peki rehmwi komwi en kasamwo kiht ni kupwur meleilei. Komw kupwurei kiht sapwellimomwi ladu kat oh kompoakepahmwi Depit.”
\p 
\v 9 Nein Depit mwahnakapw ko patohwanlahng Napal rahnmwahu wet oh pekipek wet ni mwaren Depit. Irail eri awiawih en ohlo pasapeng wasao.
\v 10 Napal ahpw sapeng irail, mahsanih, “Depit? Ihs ohl menen? I sohte kin rong ohl menen! Sahpwet direkilahr lidu kan me kin tangasang ar soumas akan.
\v 11 I sohte pahn ale kenei pilawa oh nimei pihl, oh sihpw kan me I kemehiongehr nei sounsehk sihpw kan, I ahpw pahn uhd kamwengehki aramas ekei me I sehse wasa re kohsang ie!”
\p 
\v 12 Nein Depit mwahnakapw ko eri pwurala reh oh padahkihong soahng koaros me Napal mahsanihong irail.
\v 13 Depit ahpw mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail kaunopada noumwail kedlahs akan!” Irail eri kaunopada. Depit pil kaunopada nah kedlahs oh wahda nah ohl kerenieng pahpwiki, a e kihdi ohl riepwiki pwe re en sinsile arail dipwisou kan.
\p 
\v 14 Emen en Napal eh ladu ko ahpw ndaiong en Napal eh pwoud Apikail, “Ke rongehr rohngo? Depit kadarodo meninkeder kei sang nan sapwtehn pwe re en rahnmwahwih ata soumas, e ahpw kasaroweiraildi.
\v 15 Ahpw re inenen kadekohng kiht, re sohte mwahn liderei kiht, oh sohte mehkot pirapasang reht ni ahnsou me se mihmi nansapwo sinsile sihpw.
\v 16 Re apwalih kiht ni rahn oh nipwong erein ahnsou me se mihmi rehrail oh iang apwahpwalih nait pelinmen kan.
\v 17 Menlau medewehda dahme kitail pahn wia. Pwe met pahn kakete kahrehda apwal laud ong atail soumas oh ong eh peneinei koaros. E inenen lemei kahrehda e sohte pahn men rong emen aramas!”
\p 
\v 18 Apikail mwadangete kihpene lopwon en pilawa riepwiki, ehd en wain riau, sihpw limmen me umwdahr, ehd en wahn kohn kereng riau, kapakap en wahn wain epwiki oh keik pik madekeng riepwiki, e ahpw kidahng pohn ahs ekei.
\v 19 E ahpw ndalahng nah ladu ko, “Kumwail tiengwei, I ahpw pahn idawehnkumwailwei.” E sohte mweseiseikihong eh pwoudo ire wet.
\p 
\v 20 E dakedake were ahso kohla ni ahl me wet kohdihla ni keilen dohlo, e ahpw kasaingdi Depit oh nah ohl ako me kohkohdo nanialo.
\v 21 Depit wie mengimengloalki, “Ia kahrepen ei apwahpwalih en lahpo dipwisou kan nan sapwtehnet? Sohte eh mehkot me pirapala, oh ih duwen eh kasapahldohng ie sawas me I wiahiong.
\v 22 Koht en ketin kemeiehla ma I sohte pahn kemehla aramas pwuko koaros nimenseng wet.”
\p 
\v 23 Ahnsou me Apikail kilangada Depit, e mwadangete keredihsang pohn were ahso oh poaridiong nanpwel mwohn nehn Depit kan
\v 24 oh patohwanohng, “Maing, komw ketin karonge ie mahs. Ngehi me pahn pwukoahki ire wet.
\v 25 Komw dehr tehk Napal, ohl mwahl emen! E pwungehngete edeo, me wehwehki pweipwei! I sohte pato mwo ni ahnsou me noumwi ladu ko leledo.
\v 26 KAUN-O me ketin kolokol komwi pwe komwi en dehr dupukohng omwi imwintihti kan oh kemeirailla. Eri, met I kahukihla ni mwaren KAUN-O me ketin ieias me omwi imwintihti oh koaros me men kauweikomwihla pahn ale kalokolok duwehte Napal.
\v 27 Maing, komw ketikihda kisakis wet me I patohwandohng komwi oh komw ketikihong sapwellimomwi ohl akan.
\v 28 Maing, komw ketin kupwur mahk ma mie sapwung ehu me I patohwan wiadahr. KAUN-O pahn ketin wiahkinkomwihla nanmwarki, oh pil kadaudokomwi kan, pwehki omwi ketin mahmahwenki sapwellime mahwen kan; oh komw sohte pahn wiahda sapwung erein omwi mour.
\v 29 Ma mie mehmen me pahn peiong komwi oh song en kemeikomwihla, KAUN-O, omwi Koht, pahn ketin doareikomwihla, oh sinsilei komwi, rasehng aramas emen me kin apwahpwalih nah dipwisou kesempwal. Ahpw ong omwi imwintihti kan, e pahn ketin keseirailla, duwehte aramas eh kin kapihrala takai sang nan nah pahi.
\v 30 Oh ahnsou me KAUN-O pahn ketin kapwaiada soahng mwahu koaros me e ketin inoukihong komwi oh ketin kasapwiladahng komwi nanmwarkien Israel,
\v 31 eri komw sohte pahn kupwur toutoukihla de koluhkihla omwi pahn kakerehdi nta ni sohte kahrepe oh dupukohng aramas soahng suwed kan me re wiahiong komwi. Oh ni ahnsou me KAUN-O pahn ketin kupwuramwahwihkomwihla, maing, komw dehr melieiehla.”
\p 
\v 32 Depit ahpw patohwanohng, “Kaping ong KAUN-O, Koht en Israel, me ketin poaroneikomwihdo pwehn tuhwong ie.
\v 33 Kalahngan en Koht pwehki omwi kupwuramwahu oh dahme komw wiadahr rahnwet pwe I en dehr wiahda sapwung laud en kemehla aramas oh I en dehr dupukohng ar wiewia suwed ong ie.
\v 34 KAUN-O ketin kasileiehdi pwe I en dehr kauweiukala. Eri, I kahukihla ni mwaren Koht ieias en Israel me ma komw sohte mwadangodo tuhwong ie, nein Napal ohl koaros uhdahn pahn mehla nimensenget!”
\v 35 Depit eri ale soahng koaros me liho wadohng, e ahpw ndahng liho, “Eri, komw sapahlwei oh dehr pwunod. I pahn kapwaiada dahme komw anahne.”
\p 
\v 36 Apikail eri pwurala rehn Napal, me patopato ni imweo wiewia lapalahn kamadipw ehu me konehngete nanmwarki men. E ahpw sakaula douluhl, oh nsensenamwahu. Apikail sohte ndahng mehkot lao lel nimenseng.
\v 37 Mwurin sakauo eh sarasangehr nimenseng, liho ahpw ndahng mehkoaros. Rohng wet lelete Napal kauwehla eh mohngiong oh kamwotorehla paliwereo.
\v 38 Mwurin rahn eisek KAUN-O ahpw ketin kaloke Napal, e ahpw mehla.
\p 
\v 39 Ahnsou me Depit rongada me Napal melahr, e ahpw patohwan, “Kaping ong KAUN-O me ketin doareiehla sang widing en Napal oh ketin sileiehdi sang wiahda sapwung. KAUN-O ketin kalokehki Napal eh wiewia suwed.”
\p Depit eri kadaralahng Apikail pekipek en pwopwoud.
\v 40 Nah ladu ko eri wahla ileko nan Karmel oh patohwanohng Apikail, “Depit kadarkitodo pwe se en ale komwi oh patohwanlahng reh pwe komwi en wiahla eh pwoud.”
\p 
\v 41 Apikail eri poaridiong nanpwel oh patohwan, “Iet sapwellimomwi lidu me onopadahr en widen nehn sapwellime ladu kan.”
\v 42 Ih eri uhdahte karadahng pohn were ahso. Sounpapah limmen me iangada, re ahpw iangala nein Depit ladu ko oh liho wiahla en Depit eh pwoud.
\p 
\v 43 Depit pwoudikidahr Ahinoam, mehn Sesreel, oh met e pil pwoudikihda Apikail.
\v 44 Sohl ahpw kihong Maikal, sapwellime serepein me pwoudiki Depit, en pwoudikihla Palti nein Lais, sang nan kahnimw Kallim. \x - \xo 25:44 \xt 2 Sam. 3.14-16.\x*
\c 26
\s1 Depit Pwurehng Kapitala Sohl
\p 
\v 1 Ohl ekei sang Sip ahpw kohdo rehn Sohl nan Kipea oh padahkihong me Depit wie rukuruk nin Nahna Akila ni imwin sapwtehn en Sudia.\x - \xo 26:1 \xt Mel. 54 Title.\x*
\v 2 Sohl eri mwadangete ketila Sip iangahki sounpei koahiek silipwiki en Israel pwehn rapahki Depit,
\v 3 re ahpw kauwada imwarail impwal kan limwahn ahl nin Nahna Akila. Depit mihmihte nan sapwtehno. Eri, ni eh rongada me Sohl kodohn rapahki,
\v 4 e ahpw kadarala lipoahrok kei oh diarada me mehlel pwoat me Sohl ketiket wasao.
\v 5 E ahpw mwadangala oh rapahki wasa me Sohl oh Apner nein Ner, kaunen sapwellime sounpei ko kin seiseimwok ie. Sohl kin seimwok masloalen kahnimpwalo, oh sapwellime ohl akan kin kapilpene.
\p 
\v 6 Depit eri idek rehn Ahimelek mehn Id, oh Apisai rien Sohap (ara nohno iei Seruaia), “Ihs rehmwa me pahn iang ie kohla nan kahnimpwalo?”
\p Apisai eri sapeng, nda, “Ngehi me pahn iang.”
\p 
\v 7 Eri, nipwongo Depit oh Apisai ahpw kohla pedolong nan kahnimpwal en Sohl, ira ahpw diarada Sohl e wie seiseimwok masloalen kahnimpwalo oh sapwellime ketieuwo uhdahsang nanpwel limwahn moangeo. Apner oh sapwellime sounpei ko wie memeir limwah.
\v 8 Apisai ahpw ndahng Depit, “Koht ketikihongehr omwi imwintihti pahn omwi manaman pwohnget. Eri met, mweidohng ie I en doakoahki pein sapwellime ketieu en pwar paliwere oh ilewediong nanpwel ni doak ehute—I sohte pahn pil doak pak riau!’.
\p 
\v 9 Depit ahpw patohwan, “Ke sohte pahn wiahiong mehkot suwed! KAUN-O pahn uhdahn ketin kaloke mehmen me pahn wiahiong sapwellime nanmwarki pilipil mehkot suwed.
\v 10 Depit eri usehla koasoia, “Ni mwaren Koht ieias, I ese me KAUN-O pahn pein ketin kemehla Sohl, ni eh pahn mehla ni uhdahn rahnen eh mehla de e pahn mehla nan mahwen.
\v 11 KAUN-O sohte ketin mweidohng I en song en kauwehla ih me KAUN-O ketin wiahkilahr nanmwarki! Kita wahda sapwellime ketieu en oh sapwellime sahen pihlen, oh kohkohla.”\x - \xo 26:11 \xt 1 Sam. 24.26.\x*
\v 12 Depit eri wahda sapwellime ketieuwo oh sahen pihlo sang limwahn moangen Sohlo. Depit oh Apisai eri kohkohla. Sohte emen me kilang de ese dahme wiawi de pil kehnda nipwongo—irail koaros meir kelik, pwehki KAUN-O eh ketin kameirkelikihirailla koaros.
\p 
\v 13 Depit eri kotehla wahuo kolahng pohn dohlo, wasa doh,
\v 14 e ahpw likwerkilahng sapwellimen Sohl sounpei ko oh Apner, “Apner! Ke kak rong ngilei?”
\p Apner ahpw idek, “Ihs me katakatairong oh kapiradahr nanmwarki?”
\p 
\v 15 Depit ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Apner, kaidehn komwi ohl me keieu ndand nan Israel? Eri, dahme komw sohte sinsilehki omw soumas, nanmwarkio? Mie me ahpwtehn pedolong nan kahnimpwalo pwehn kemehla omwi soumaso.
\v 16 Omwi pwukoa sohte pweida, Apner! I kahukihla ni mwaren KAUN-O me ketin ieias me kumwail koaros konehng en kamakamala, pwehki amwail sohte sile mwahu amwail soumas, me KAUN-O ketin wiahkihla nanmwarki. Kumwail kilang! Ia sapwellimen nanmwarkio ketieuwo? Ia sahen pihl me mihmi limwahn tapwio?”
\p 
\v 17 Sohl eri tehkada ngilen Depit oh kalelapak, “Depit, kowe men, samwa?”
\p Depit ahpw sapeng, “Ei maing, Wasa Lapalap.”
\v 18 E ahpw usehla koasoia, “Maing, dahme komwi pwakipwakih kin ie, sapwellimomwi ladu menet? Dahme I wiadahr? Soangen sapwung dah me I wiadahr?
\v 19 Maing, Wasa Lapalap, komw ketin karonge mahs dahme I pahn patohwan. Ma KAUN-O me ketin kupwurehda komwi en uhwong ie, ehu meirong ong ih pahn kahrehda eh pahn ketin wekidala kupwure; ahpw ma sang ni koasoandien aramas met, eri, sapwellimen KAUN-O keria en kohdiong pohrail. Pwehki ar pwakihiesang nin limmen KAUN-O oh pwakihielahng nan ehu sahpw wasa me I pahn kin kakete kaudokiong koht en liki kan.
\v 20 Komw dehr mweidohng ie I en mehla nan sapwen mehn liki kan, wasa me dohsang KAUN-O. Dahme nanmwarkien Israel ketidohn kemehkihla soangen aramas duwete ngehi, me rasehng kisin likarak kis? Dahme e sasaingkinieseli duwehte menpihr lawalo men?”
\v 21 Sohl eri sapeng, mahsanih, “I wiadahr mehkot sapwung, pwurodo samwa! I solahr pahn pwurehng wiahiong uhk mehkot suwed, pwehki omw sohte kemeiehla pwohnget. I wiadahr mwomwen aramas pweipwei! I wiadahr mehkot suwed!”
\p 
\v 22 Depit ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Maing, Wasa Lapalap, iet sapwellimomwi ketieuwo. Komw ketin mweidohng emen sapwellimomwi ohl akan en patohdo oh patohwanda.
\v 23 KAUN-O kin ketin katingih irail kan me kin loalopwoat oh pwung. E ketikihdiong komwi pahn ei manaman rahnwet, ahpw I sohte wiahiong komwi mehkot ih me KAUN-O ketin wiahkilahr nanmwarki.
\v 24 Pwehki ei sohte kemeikomwihla rahnwet, KAUN-O en pil ketin wiahiong ie soahngohte oh ketin kasaledekihiehla sang apwal koaros!”
\p 
\v 25 Sohl ahpw mahsanihong Depit, “Koht en ketin kupwuramwahwihiuk, samwa! Ke pahn pweida ni soahng koaros me ke pahn wia!”
\p Depit eri mwesel dodouluhlla, oh Sohl sapahllahng ni uhdakeo.
\c 27
\s1 Depit Nanpwungen mehn Pilisdia kan
\p 
\v 1 Depit eri mengimengloalki, “Ehu rahn pwukat Sohl pahn kemeiehla. Ihte me keieu mwahu I en tangalahng Pilisdia. Eri, Sohl pahn sohla rapahkin ie nan Israel, I ahpw sohte pahn diar apwal.”
\v 2 Depit oh nah ohl wenepwikio eri mwadangete mweselahng rehn Akis nein Maok, nanmwarkien Kad.
\v 3 Depit oh nah ohl ako eri kousoanla nan Kad iangahki arail peneinei kan. Depit oh eh pwoud riemeno iang ih, Ahinoam sang Sesreel, oh Apikail, en Napal me melahro eh pwoud, sang Karmel.
\v 4 Ni Sohl eh karongehda me Depit sopolahngehr nan Kad, e ahpw sohla rapahki.
\p 
\v 5 Depit eri ndahng Akis, “Ma komwi kompoakepahi, eri komw mweidohng ie ehu kisin kahnimw en pwe I en kousoan loale. Maing, sohte anahnepen I en iang komwi kousoan nan poahsoan kaunen kahnimwet.”
\v 6 Akis eri ketikihong kisin kahnimw Siklak, ih kahrepe wet me nanmwarkien Suda sapwellimanikihla kisin kahnimw Siklak.
\v 7 Depit koukousoanki nan Pilisdia erein sounpwong eisek weneu.
\p 
\v 8 Erein ahnsowo Depit oh nah ohl ako kin mahweniong tohn Kesur, Kirsi, oh Amalek, me koukousoan nan sahpwo ahnsou reirei. E kin mahweniong sahpwo lao lellahng Sur, oh pil leldilahng nan Isip,
\v 9 kemekemehla ohl oh lih koaros oh kin wahsang neirail sihpw, kou, ahs, kamel, oh pil arail likou kan. E ahpw pahn kin pwurodo rehn Akis,
\v 10 me kin kalelapak reh, “Ia wasa ke mahwen ie met?” Depit eri kin ndahng me e kohla palieir en Suda de nan sapwen kadaudok en Serameel de nan sahpw wasa me mehn Ken kan kin kousoan ie.
\v 11 Depit eri kin kemehla koaros, ohl oh lih, pwe emen irail de pwurala nan Kad oh ndahda dahme ih oh nah ohl ako wiadahr. Ih met me Depit kin wiewia nindokon eh koukousoan nan Pilisdia.
\v 12 Ahpw Akis kin likih Depit oh kin mengimengloalki, “E pahn uhpah ie erein eh mour pwehki kiseh mehn Israel kan ar kailongki.”
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 Kedekedeo, mehn Pilisdia ko kapokonepene neirail karis en sounpei kan pwe re en mahweniong Israel. Eri, Akis ahpw mahsanihong Depit, “Komw mwahngih me komwi oh noumwi sounpei kan pahn iang ie mahweniong mehn Israel kan.”
\p 
\v 2 Depit ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Ei maing, omwi ladu ngehi, oh komw pahn mwahngih dahme I kak wiahda.”
\p Akis eri mahsanih, “Me mwahu! I pahn wiahkin komwi silepen paliwereiet.”
\s1 Sohl Ale Kaweid rehn Sounkapwour Eni men
\p 
\v 3 Eri, Samuel melahr, oh mehn Israel koaros mwahieiki oh sarepedi nan sousou ni imweo nan Rama. A Sohl ketin kasarehla sounwunahni oh sounkapwour eni koaros sang Israel.\x - \xo 28:3 \xt 1 Sam 25.1.\x*\x - \xo 28:3 \xt Lip 20.27; Deud. 18.10-11.\x*
\p 
\v 4 Eri, karis en mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw pokonpene oh kauwada imwarail impwal kan limwahn kahnimw Sunem. Sohl ahpw ketin kapokonepene mehn Israel ko oh kauweda sapwellime kahnimpwal nin Nahna Kilpoa.
\v 5 Eri, ahnsou me Sohl mahsanihada karis en mehn Pilisdia ko, e inenen masepwehkada.
\v 6 Ih eri idek rehn KAUN-O dahme e pahn patohwan wia. Ahpw KAUN-O sohte mwahn ketin sapeng sang nan ouraman, de sang ni takai sarawi ko, Urim oh Dumim, de sang rehn soukohp akan.\x - \xo 28:6 \xt Nemp 27.21.\x*
\v 7 Ihme Sohl mahsanihkihong sapwellime lapalap ako, “Kumwail rapahkihdo emen lih sounkapwour eni, pwe I en kowohng kadierekada sang reh duwen ei pweh.”
\p Irail eri sapengki, “Mie mehmen nan Endor.”
\p 
\v 8 Sohl eri wekidala mwomwe; e ketin pwuhriong nan soangen likou tohrohr kei. E ahpw ketida nipwong iangahki riemen sapwellime sounpei ko pwe en ketilahng tuhwong liho. E ahpw mahsanihong liho, “Wilianiehdi mahs oh idek rehn ngehn kan oh ndadohng ie dahme pahn pweida. Kapwourada ngenen ohl me I pahn ndawei ede.”
\p 
\v 9 Liho ahpw sapeng nda, “Komw dehdehki mwahu dahme Nanmwarki Sohl wiadahr, duwen eh ketin kasare sang nan Israel sounwunahni kan oh pil sounkapwour eni kan. Eri, dahme komw songosongki en widingeiehdi oh kemeiehla?”
\p 
\v 10 Sohl eri ketin wiahiong liho inou sarawi oh kahukihla, mahsanih, “Ni mwaren KAUN-O me ieias, I inoukihong uhk me ke sohte pahn ale lokolok pwehki irair wet.”
\p 
\v 11 Liho eri idek, “Ihs me I pahn kapwourodohng komwi?”
\p Sohl ahpw ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “Samuel.”\x - \xo 28:11 \xt Sir 46.20.\x*
\p 
\v 12 Ni liho eh kilangada Samuel, e tapihada weriwer. E ahpw patohwanohng Sohl, “Dahme komw ketin pitihekin ie? Pwe iei komwi Nanmwarki Sohl!”
\p 
\v 13 Nanmwarkio ahpw mahsanihong, “Ke dehr masak. Dahme ke kilikilang?”
\p A e sapeng, patohwan, “I patopatohwan ngehn ehu me kohkohda sang nan pwehl.”
\p 
\v 14 Sohl ahpw keinemwe, “Ia mwomwe?”
\p Liho ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “E mwomwen ohl laud emen, me kidikidki lapalahn tehi ehu.”
\p Sohl eri mwahngihada me iei ih Samuel. E ahpw poaridi lel nanpwel.
\p 
\v 15 Samuel eri patohwanlahng Sohl, “Dahme komw kedirepwahkiniedahr? Ia kahrepen omwi malipeiehdo?”
\p Sohl ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “I inenen pwunodadahr kowahlap! Mehn Pilisdia kan wie mahmahweniong ie, oh Koht ketin likidmelieielahr. E solahr ketin sapeng ie, sang sapwellime soukohp akan de sang ni ouraman. Ih kahrepen ei likwerihkomwihdo, pwe komwi en mahsanihong ie dahme I pahn wia.”
\p 
\v 16 Samuel ahpw patohwan, “Dahme komw likwerihkin ie, ni KAUN-O eh ketin keseikomwilahr oh wialahr omwi imwintihti?
\v 17 KAUN-O ketin wiahiongkomwier dahme e ketin koasoanehdi me I usehiong komwio: e ketiki sang rehmwi wehio oh uhd ketikihong Depit.\x - \xo 28:17 \xt 1 Sam 15.28.\x*
\v 18 Pwe komwi sohte peikiong kamwomwala douluhl mehn Amalek ko oh mehkoaros me re ahneki. Ih kahrepen en KAUN-O eh ketin wiewiahiong komwi soahng wet.\x - \xo 28:18 \xt 1 Sam 15.3-9.\x*
\v 19 E pahn ketin pangala komwi oh mehn Israel kan rehn mehn Pilisdia kan. Lakapw komwi oh noumwi pwutak kan pahn iangiehla, oh KAUN-O pahn pil ketin pangala karis en Israel kan rehn mehn Pilisdia kan.”
\p 
\v 20 Ni ahnsowohte Sohl pah lempehdiong nanpwel oh wonohn wasao, rerrerki eh masepwehk pwehki en Samuel koasoio. E inenen luwetala, pwehki eh sohte konote mehkot ni rahno oh nipwongo pwon.
\v 21 Liho ahpw patohla reh oh kilangada duwen eh wie rerrerki eh masepwehk, e ahpw patohwanohng, “Maing, komw kupwur mahk. I kereniong kauwehla ei mour ni ei wiahda me komw ketin pekien.
\v 22 Eri met, komw ketin kupwure ei pekipeket. Mie met konotomwi, komw konote pwe komwi en rosonda oh kak seiloak.”
\p 
\v 23 Sohl ahpw ketin mahsanihong me e sohte pahn konote mehkot. A sapwellime lapalap ako pil patohwan koangngoangehki en konot. Eri mwuhr, e ahpw meleileidi, oh ketida sang nanpwel oh ketidi ong pohn peht ehu.
\v 24 Liho eri mwadangete kemehla koupwul men me e kin kamwekamwenge. E ahpw ale pilawa kei, kaunopada, oh umwunda pilawa kei me sohte doal ihs.
\v 25 E ahpw patohwandi konot oko mwohn Sohl oh sapwellime lapalap ko; irail eri konotala, oh mwesel nipwongohte.
\c 29
\s1 Mehn Pilisdia Soikala Depit
\p 
\v 1 Mehn Pilisdia kan kapokonepene neirail karis koaros nan Apek, nindokon mehn Israel kan ar kauwada imwarail impwal kan ni pwarer en Wahun Sesreel.
\v 2 Nanmwarki limmen en Pilisdia ko eri mwekidida iangahki nair pwihn kei me wad epwiki oh ekei pwihn wad kid; Depit oh nah ohl ako idawehnirailla iangala Nanmwarki Akis.
\v 3 Kaunen Pilisdia ko kilangirailda oh idekda, “Dahme mehn Ipru pwukat wiewia met?”
\p Akis ahpw sapeng irail, mahsanih, “Ih Depit met, sapwellimen Sohl mehn Israel, lapalapo. E patopatohier rehi ekis wereilahr. E sohte wiahda sapwung ehu rehi sang rahn me e patohdo rehi.”
\p 
\v 4 Ahpw mehn Pilisdia ko lingeringerda pahn Akis oh patohwanohng, “Komw kapwurehla ohl menen nan eh wasa; komw dehr mweidohng en iang mahwen pwe e de wekidekte uhwong kitail nan mahwen. Sohte mehkot tohrohr e kak wia pwehn ale keniken pahn eh soumas, pwe ihte kamakamalahn nait aramas akan.
\v 5 Pwe ih Depito met, me lih akan kin kahkahlek oh kokoulki, ‘Sohl kemehla kid, a Depit kemehla nen.’”\x - \xo 29:5 \xt 1 Sam. 18.7; 21.11.\x*
\p 
\v 6 Akis eri malipehdo Depit oh mahsanihong, “I kahukihla ni mwaren Koht ieias en Israel me komw uhdahn loalopwoatohng ie; oh I pahn perenki ma komw pahn iang ie nan mahwen wet. Sohte sapwung ehu I diarada rehmwi sang rahn me komw ketido rehi. Ahpw nanmwarki teikan sohte kupwurki omwi ieiang ie.
\v 7 Eri, komw meleilei sapahlla nan omwi wasa, oh dehr wia mehkot me pahn kauwehla kupwurarail.”
\p 
\v 8 Depit ahpw sapeng patohwan, “Maing, sapwung da me I patohwan wiadahr? Ma nin duwen omwi mahsanih me komwi sohte diarada sapwung ehu rehi sang ni rahn me I tapihada papah komwi, dahme I sohte pahn iang kin komwi, ei soumas oh nanmwarki, oh iang mahweniong sapwellimomwi imwintihti kan?”
\p 
\v 9 Akis ketin sapeng, mahsanih, “I pwungki. I wiahkin komwi aramas loalopwoat duwehte tohnleng en Koht men. Ahpw nanmwarki teikan mahsaniher me komw sohte kak iang ie mahwen.
\v 10 Eri, maing Depit, nimenseng en lakapw kumwail koaros me patohdo sang rehn Sohl oh patohdo rehi, kumwail pahn pwourda mwadang oh mwesel mwohn ketipin eh pahn dak.”
\p 
\v 11 Depit oh nah sounpei ko eri mweselda nin sohrahn en mandahn rahno pwurala Pilisdia, oh mehn Pilisdia ko patopatohla Sesreel.
\c 30
\s1 Mahwen ong mehn Amalek kan
\p 
\v 1 Mwurin rahn riau Depit oh nah sounpei ko lel Siklak. Mehn Amalek ko mahweniongehr palieir en Suda oh Siklak. Re isikala kahnimwo
\v 2 oh koledi lih koaros; re sohte kemeirailla, pwe re aleirailte wahda ni ar mweselsang mwo.
\v 3 Ahnsou me Depit oh nah sounpei ko lel mwo, re diarada duwen kahnimwo eh isihslahr oh ar pwoud kan, nair pwutak kan oh serepein kan ar wisiksangehr.
\v 4 Depit oh nah sounpei ko ahpw tapihada sengiseng oh sohte tokedi lao re ngirala.
\v 5 En Depit eh pwoud riemeno, Ahinoam oh Apikail, pil iang wisiksang.\x - \xo 30:5 \xt 1 Sam. 25.42-43.\x*
\p 
\v 6 Depit milahr nan apwal laud, pwehki nah aramas ako ar lingeringerkidahr nair seri ko ar solahr mie, re koasoakoasoaneier re en katehki takai; KAUN-O eri ketin kakehlahda nan kapehde.
\v 7 Depit eri patohwanohng samworo Apaiadar nein Ahimelek, “Komw patohwando mahs likou ihpodo.”\x - \xo 30:7 \xt 1 Sam. 22.20-23.\x*
\v 8 Depit eri kalelapak rehn KAUN-O, “Maing, I en pwakihala irail ko me kauwehla kahnimwo? I pahn kak koanoairaildi?”
\p KAUN-O ketin sapeng, “Ei, pwakihiralla; ke pahn koanoairaildi oh kapitala me lohdi kan.”
\p 
\v 9 Depit oh nah sounpei wenepwikio ahpw mweselda oh ni ar lel ni Piletik Pesor, ekei sounpei ko mwohndi wasao.
\v 10 Depit eri douluhlla iangahki sounpei pahpwiki; me riepwikio inenen pwangada mehlel oh sohla kak iang kotehla pihlo; irail ahpw mwohndi wasao.
\v 11 Sounpei ko me iang Depit ahpw diarada kisin pwutak en Isip men nansapwo oh wadohng Depit. Re ahpw kihong kisin mwenge, pihl,
\v 12 iangahki pik madekeng oh dunen wahn wain riau. Mwurin kisin pwutako eh mwengeier, e ahpw kehlailda; pwe rahn siluh me e sohte mwenge oh nimpil.
\v 13 Depit ahpw idek reh, “Ihs omw soumas, oh ke kohsang ia?”
\p A kisin pwutako sapeng, patohwan, “Ngehi men Isip, lidun mehn Amalek men. Ei soumaso keseiehla rahn siluh douwer powe pwehki ei soumwahuda.
\v 14 Se patohwan mahweniong sapwen mehn Kered kan ni palieir en Suda oh sapwen peneineien Kalep, kiht eri isikala kahnimw Siklak.”
\p 
\v 15 Depit ahpw idek reh, “Ke kak kahreielahng rehn irail ko me isikala kahnimwo?”
\p A kisin pwutako sapeng, patohwan, “I pahn kahreikomwihla, ma komw pahn inoukihong ie ni mwaren Koht me komw sohte pahn kemeiehla de kapwureielahng rehn ei soumas.”
\v 16 Kisin pwutako eri karehla Depit rehrail.
\p Aramas suwed ko mwomwohdseli wasao, mwengemwenge, niminim sakau, oh kamakamadipw pwehki uwen laud en dipwisou me lohdi sang mehn Pilisdia oh Suda.
\v 17 Nin sohrahn en mandasang rahno Depit oh nah sounpei ko eri mahweniong irail lao lel nin soutik. Sohte emen irail pitla, likin mwahnakapw pahpwiki me dake kamel oh tangdoaui.
\v 18 Depit eri kapitala aramas koaros oh mehkoaros me mehn Amalek ko wahsang, e pil kapitala eh pwoud riemeno;
\v 19 sohte mehkot me re sohte kapwurehdo. E kapwurehdo nein nah ohl ako koaros neirail pwutak kan oh serepein kan oh mehkoaros me mehn Amalek ko wahsang.
\v 20 E pil kapwurehdo nair pelinmen kan koaros; ohl ako ahpw kahkahre pelinmen ko mwohrail oh koasoakoasoia, “Mepwukat koaros sapwellimen Depit.”
\p 
\v 21 Depit eri pwurala rehn sounpei riepwikio me luwetala sohla kak iang ih oh mwohndi ni Piletik Pesor. Irail eri kohdo kasamwo Depit oh nah sounpei ko, Depit eri keilahng mparail oh rahnmwahwih irail ni nsenamwahu.
\v 22 Ahpw ohl lemei oh soh katepe kei me iang Depit ahpw nda, “Re sohte iang kitail kohla mahwen, eri kitail sohte pahn kihong irail mehkot sang nan dipwisou lohdi kan. Re kak ale arail pwoud oh neirail seri kan oh kohkohla.”
\p 
\v 23 Ahpw Depit sapeng irail, ketihtihki, “Riei ko, kitail sohte kak wia soahnget ong dahme KAUN-O ketikihong kitail. E ketin doareikitailla oh ketikihong kitail pwe kitail en powehdi aramas suwed pwuko.
\v 24 Sohte me kak pwungki dahme kumwail koasoakoasoane. Koaruhsie pahn iang ahneki mehkot: me mwohndi ko me sohte iang mahwen pahn iang ahneki mehkot duwehte me kohla iang mahwen.”
\v 25 Depit wiahkihla met kosonned ehu, oh mehn Israel koaros kin idawehn kosonned wet sang ahnsowo kohdo lel rahnwet.
\p 
\v 26 Ahnsou me Depit pwurala Siklak, e kadaralahng kompoakepah ko, kaunen Suda ko, ekei kepwe sang ni kepwe lohdi ko, iangahki pato pwukat, “Iet kisakis ong kumwail sang ni dipwisou kan me lohdi sang sapwellimen KAUN-O imwintihti kan.”
\v 27 E kadaralahng aramas en Pedel, ong mehn Rama ni palieir en Suda, ong aramas en kahnimw kan en Sattir,
\v 28 Aroer, Sipmod, Estemoa,
\v 29 oh Rakal; ong peneineien Serameel, ong mehn Ken
\v 30 oh ong mehn kahnimw kan en Orma, Porasan, Adak,
\v 31 oh Epron. E kadaralahng wasa koaros me ih oh nah sounpei ko mihmihseli ie.
\c 31
\s1 Sipallahn Sohl oh Sapwellime Pwutak ko
\r (1 Kronikel 10.1-12)
\p 
\v 1 Eri, mahwen ahpw pweida nanpwungen mehn Pilisdia oh mehn Israel nin Nahna Kilpoa. Mehn Israel tohtohie me kamakamala wasao, oh me luhwehdi ko koaros re tangdoaui.
\v 2 Mehn Pilisdia ko eri pwakihala Sohl oh sapwellime pwutak ko. Re ahpw kemehla sapwellime pwutak Sonadan, Apinadap, oh Malkisuha.
\v 3 Peio inenen mwuledek limwahn Sohl. Kanengen keseik ketieu kei lel Sohl, e ahpw ohkihla laud oh kereniong mehkihla.
\v 4 Ih eri mahsanihong mwahnakapw men me kin weuwa sapwellime tehtehn mahwen ko, “Usasang noumw kedlahsen nan kidipe, oh kemeiehla, pwe mehn Pilisdia rotorot pwukat de kepitikin ie oh kemeiehla.” Ahpw mwahnakapwo inenen masak wia soangen irair wet. Sohl eri ketin usada pein sapwellime kedlahso, oh pein lukupoardiong powe.
\v 5 Ni mwahnakapwo eh kilang Sohl eh melahr, e pil pein lukupoardiong pohn nah kedlahso oh iang Sohl mehla.
\v 6 Ih duwen Sohl eh sipalla iangahki sapwellime pwutak silimeno oh mwahnakapwo; sapwellimen Sohl sounpei ko koaros mehla rahno.
\v 7 Ni ahnsou me mehn Israel kan me mihmi palio Wahun Sesreel oh palimesehn Pillap Sordan ar esehda me karis en mehn Israel ko tangehrdoaui, oh Sohl oh sapwellime pwutak ko melahr, re tangasang nan ar kahnimw kan. Mehn Pilisdia ko ahpw uhd kohla oh kousoanla nan kahnimw ko.
\p 
\v 8 Manda sang rahnen mahweno, mehn Pilisdia ko kohla pwe re en kihsang tehtehn mahwen ko rehn kahlep en me melahr ako. Re ahpw diarada kahlep en Sohl oh sapwellime pwutak ko ar wonohn nin Nahna Kilpoa.
\v 9 Irail eri lupukasang tapwin Sohl oh wahda, iangahki sapwellime tehtehn mahwen ko. Re ahpw pakairkihla rohng pwoatet Pilisdia—re pil kadarala meninkeder kei pwe re en pakairkihong ar koht akan oh aramas akan.
\v 10 Irail ahpw langadahng tehtehn mahwen ko nan tehnpas en koht lih Asdarde, oh pasurediong paliweren Sohl ni kelen kahnimw Ped San.
\p 
\v 11 Eri, ni aramas en Sapes, nan Kilead, rongada duwen me mehn Pilisida ko wiahiong Sohl,
\v 12 ohl me keieu kommwad kei ahpw mweselda, re kohkohla nipwongo pwon lao lel Ped San. Re kohla oh kihdi sang kahlep en Sohl oh sapwellime pwutak ko ni kehlo. Re ahpw wahla Sapes oh isikala ie.
\v 13 Re ahpw ale tihrail ko oh sarepedi pahn tuhke damarisk pwoat nan kahnimwo. Irail eri kaisihsolki erein rahn isuh. 
